<div class="proof-box">
<strong>主要公式の証明：</strong><br>
<strong>① <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mo>sin</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mi>′</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>cos</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">(\sin x)&#39;=\cos x</annotation></semantics></math>：</strong>
<math display="block" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mo>sin</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mi>′</mi><mo>=</mo><munder><mo>lim</mo><mrow><mi>h</mi><mo>→</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></munder><mfrac><mrow><mo>sin</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>h</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>−</mo><mo>sin</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow><mi>h</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><munder><mo>lim</mo><mrow><mi>h</mi><mo>→</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></munder><mfrac><mrow><mn>2</mn><mo>cos</mo><mspace width="-0.167em"></mspace><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mi>h</mi><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>sin</mo><mfrac><mi>h</mi><mn>2</mn></mfrac></mrow><mi>h</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><munder><mo>lim</mo><mrow><mi>h</mi><mo>→</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></munder><mo>cos</mo><mspace width="-0.167em"></mspace><mspace width="-0.167em"></mspace><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mi>h</mi><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>⋅</mo><mfrac><mrow><mo>sin</mo><mfrac><mi>h</mi><mn>2</mn></mfrac></mrow><mfrac><mi>h</mi><mn>2</mn></mfrac></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mo>cos</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>⋅</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>=</mo><mo>cos</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
(\sin x)&#39;=\lim_{h\to 0}\frac{\sin(x+h)-\sin x}{h}=\lim_{h\to 0}\frac{2\cos\!\left(x+\frac{h}{2}\right)\sin\frac{h}{2}}{h}=\lim_{h\to 0}\cos\!\!\left(x+\frac{h}{2}\right)\cdot\frac{\sin\frac{h}{2}}{\frac{h}{2}}=\cos x\cdot 1=\cos x
</annotation></semantics></math>
<strong>② <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mo>cos</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mi>′</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>−</mo><mo>sin</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">(\cos x)&#39;=-\sin x</annotation></semantics></math>：</strong>加法定理 <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>cos</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>h</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mo>cos</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>cos</mo><mi>h</mi><mo>−</mo><mo>sin</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>sin</mo><mi>h</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\cos(x+h)=\cos x\cos h-\sin x\sin h</annotation></semantics></math> より同様。<br><br>
<strong>③ <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><msup><mi>e</mi><mi>x</mi></msup><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mi>′</mi><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>e</mi><mi>x</mi></msup></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">(e^x)&#39;=e^x</annotation></semantics></math>：</strong>
<math display="block" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><msup><mi>e</mi><mi>x</mi></msup><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mi>′</mi><mo>=</mo><munder><mo>lim</mo><mrow><mi>h</mi><mo>→</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></munder><mfrac><mrow><msup><mi>e</mi><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>h</mi></mrow></msup><mo>−</mo><msup><mi>e</mi><mi>x</mi></msup></mrow><mi>h</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>e</mi><mi>x</mi></msup><munder><mo>lim</mo><mrow><mi>h</mi><mo>→</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></munder><mfrac><mrow><msup><mi>e</mi><mi>h</mi></msup><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mi>h</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>e</mi><mi>x</mi></msup><mo>⋅</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>e</mi><mi>x</mi></msup></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
(e^x)&#39;=\lim_{h\to 0}\frac{e^{x+h}-e^x}{h}=e^x\lim_{h\to 0}\frac{e^h-1}{h}=e^x\cdot 1=e^x
</annotation></semantics></math>
<strong>④ <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mo>log</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mi>′</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mn>1</mn><mi>x</mi></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">(\log x)&#39;=\dfrac{1}{x}</annotation></semantics></math>（<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>&gt;</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">x&gt;0</annotation></semantics></math>）：</strong>
<math display="block" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mo>log</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mi>′</mi><mo>=</mo><munder><mo>lim</mo><mrow><mi>h</mi><mo>→</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></munder><mfrac><mrow><mo>log</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>h</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>−</mo><mo>log</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow><mi>h</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><munder><mo>lim</mo><mrow><mi>h</mi><mo>→</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></munder><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mi>x</mi></mfrac><mo>⋅</mo><mfrac><mrow><mo>log</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mi>h</mi><mi>x</mi></mfrac><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><mfrac><mi>h</mi><mi>x</mi></mfrac></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mi>x</mi></mfrac><mo>⋅</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mi>x</mi></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
(\log x)&#39;=\lim_{h\to 0}\frac{\log(x+h)-\log x}{h}=\lim_{h\to 0}\frac{1}{x}\cdot\frac{\log(1+\frac{h}{x})}{\frac{h}{x}}=\frac{1}{x}\cdot 1=\frac{1}{x}
</annotation></semantics></math>
<strong>⑤ <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mi>n</mi></msup><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mi>′</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>n</mi><msup><mi>x</mi><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">(x^n)&#39;=nx^{n-1}</annotation></semantics></math>（<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>∈</mo><mi>ℕ</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">n\in\mathbb{N}</annotation></semantics></math>）：</strong><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msup><mi>x</mi><mi>n</mi></msup><mo>−</mo><msup><mi>a</mi><mi>n</mi></msup><mo>=</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>−</mo><mi>a</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></msup><mi>a</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>⋯</mi><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>a</mi><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">x^n-a^n=(x-a)(x^{n-1}+x^{n-2}a+\cdots+a^{n-1})</annotation></semantics></math> より：
<math display="block" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><munder><mo>lim</mo><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>→</mo><mi>a</mi></mrow></munder><mfrac><mrow><msup><mi>x</mi><mi>n</mi></msup><mo>−</mo><msup><mi>a</mi><mi>n</mi></msup></mrow><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>−</mo><mi>a</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><munder><mo>lim</mo><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>→</mo><mi>a</mi></mrow></munder><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><mo>+</mo><mi>⋯</mi><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>a</mi><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mi>n</mi><msup><mi>a</mi><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
\lim_{x\to a}\frac{x^n-a^n}{x-a}=\lim_{x\to a}(x^{n-1}+\cdots+a^{n-1})=na^{n-1}
</annotation></semantics></math>
<div class="qed">■</div>
</div>
</div><!-- /s2-1 -->

<!-- 2.2 -->

<div class="section" id="s2-2">
<h3>2.2 積・商・合成関数の微分</h3>

<div class="formula-box theorem">
<strong>三大微分法則</strong>
<math display="block" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo stretchy="false" form="prefix">{</mo><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mi>g</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo stretchy="false" form="postfix">}</mo><mi>′</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>f</mi><mi>′</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mi>g</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>+</mo><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mi>g</mi><mi>′</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mspace width="2.0em"></mspace><mtext mathvariant="normal">（積の微分）</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
\{f(x)g(x)\}&#39;=f&#39;(x)g(x)+f(x)g&#39;(x)\qquad\text{（積の微分）}
</annotation></semantics></math>
<math display="block" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">{</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><mrow><mi>g</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow></mfrac><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">}</mo></mrow><mi>′</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>f</mi><mi>′</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mi>g</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>−</mo><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mi>g</mi><mi>′</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="false" form="prefix">{</mo><mi>g</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><msup><mo stretchy="false" form="postfix">}</mo><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow></mfrac><mspace width="2.0em"></mspace><mtext mathvariant="normal">（商の微分）</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
\left\{\frac{f(x)}{g(x)}\right\}&#39;=\frac{f&#39;(x)g(x)-f(x)g&#39;(x)}{\{g(x)\}^2}\qquad\text{（商の微分）}
</annotation></semantics></math>
<math display="block" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mfrac><mi>d</mi><mrow><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow></mfrac><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>g</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mi>f</mi><mi>′</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>g</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>⋅</mo><mi>g</mi><mi>′</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mspace width="2.0em"></mspace><mtext mathvariant="normal">（合成関数・Chain Rule）</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
\frac{d}{dx}f(g(x))=f&#39;(g(x))\cdot g&#39;(x)\qquad\text{（合成関数・Chain Rule）}
</annotation></semantics></math>
</div>

<div class="proof-box">
<strong>積の微分の証明：</strong>
<math display="block" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo stretchy="false" form="prefix">{</mo><mi>f</mi><mi>g</mi><mo stretchy="false" form="postfix">}</mo><mi>′</mi><mo>=</mo><munder><mo>lim</mo><mrow><mi>h</mi><mo>→</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></munder><mfrac><mrow><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>h</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mi>g</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>h</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>−</mo><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mi>g</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><mi>h</mi></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
\{fg\}&#39;=\lim_{h\to 0}\frac{f(x+h)g(x+h)-f(x)g(x)}{h}
</annotation></semantics></math>
分子に <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>±</mo><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mi>g</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>h</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\pm f(x)g(x+h)</annotation></semantics></math> を加えて整理：
<math display="block" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>=</mo><munder><mo>lim</mo><mrow><mi>h</mi><mo>→</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></munder><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">[</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>h</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>−</mo><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><mi>h</mi></mfrac><mi>g</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>h</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>+</mo><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mfrac><mrow><mi>g</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>h</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>−</mo><mi>g</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><mi>h</mi></mfrac><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">]</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mi>f</mi><mi>′</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mi>g</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>+</mo><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mi>g</mi><mi>′</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
=\lim_{h\to 0}\left[\frac{f(x+h)-f(x)}{h}g(x+h)+f(x)\frac{g(x+h)-g(x)}{h}\right]=f&#39;(x)g(x)+f(x)g&#39;(x)
</annotation></semantics></math>
（<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mi>g</mi><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">g</annotation></semantics></math> の連続性から <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>g</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>h</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>→</mo><mi>g</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">g(x+h)\to g(x)</annotation></semantics></math>）
<div class="qed">■</div>
</div>

<div class="proof-box">
<strong>合成関数の微分の証明（概略）：</strong><br>
<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>Δ</mi><mi>u</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>g</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>h</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>−</mo><mi>g</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>≠</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\Delta u=g(x+h)-g(x)\neq 0</annotation></semantics></math> のとき：
<math display="block" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mfrac><mrow><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>g</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>h</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>−</mo><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>g</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><mi>h</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>g</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>+</mo><mi>Δ</mi><mi>u</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>−</mo><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>g</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><mrow><mi>Δ</mi><mi>u</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>⋅</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>Δ</mi><mi>u</mi></mrow><mi>h</mi></mfrac><mover><mo>→</mo><mrow><mi>h</mi><mo>→</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></mover><mi>f</mi><mi>′</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>g</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>⋅</mo><mi>g</mi><mi>′</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
\frac{f(g(x+h))-f(g(x))}{h}=\frac{f(g(x)+\Delta u)-f(g(x))}{\Delta u}\cdot\frac{\Delta u}{h}\xrightarrow{h\to 0}f&#39;(g(x))\cdot g&#39;(x)
</annotation></semantics></math>
（<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>h</mi><mo>→</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">h\to 0</annotation></semantics></math> で <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>Δ</mi><mi>u</mi><mo>→</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\Delta u\to 0</annotation></semantics></math> を利用。<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>Δ</mi><mi>u</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\Delta u=0</annotation></semantics></math> となる場合は補論が必要だが入試では上記で十分。）
<div class="qed">■</div>
</div>

<div class="tip-box">
<strong>合成関数微分のコツ：</strong>「外側を微分 × 中身はそのまま × 中身を微分」<br>
例：<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mo>sin</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mi>′</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>cos</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>⋅</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">(\sin(x^2))&#39;=\cos(x^2)\cdot 2x</annotation></semantics></math>。多重合成は内側から一層ずつ剥がす。
</div>

<div class="example-box">
<strong>例題 2.1</strong> <span class="lv lv-b">基礎</span>　次の関数を微分せよ。<br>
(1) <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>3</mn></msup><mo>sin</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">y=x^3\sin x</annotation></semantics></math> &emsp; (2) <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>e</mi><mrow><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">y=e^{x^2+1}</annotation></semantics></math> &emsp; (3) <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>log</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mo>sin</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">y=\log(\sin x)</annotation></semantics></math> &emsp; (4) <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><msup><mi>e</mi><mi>x</mi></msup><mrow><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">y=\dfrac{e^x}{x^2+1}</annotation></semantics></math> &emsp; (5) <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><msup><mo>sin</mo><mn>4</mn></msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mn>3</mn><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">y=\sin^4(3x)</annotation></semantics></math>
<div class="answer-block">
(1) 積：<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>3</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>sin</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>3</mn></msup><mo>cos</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">3x^2\sin x+x^3\cos x</annotation></semantics></math><br><br>
(2) 合成：<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msup><mi>e</mi><mrow><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><mo>⋅</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><msup><mi>e</mi><mrow><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">e^{x^2+1}\cdot 2x=2xe^{x^2+1}</annotation></semantics></math><br><br>
(3) 合成：<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mrow><mo>cos</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow><mrow><mo>sin</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mo>cot</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\dfrac{\cos x}{\sin x}=\cot x</annotation></semantics></math><br><br>
(4) 商：<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mrow><msup><mi>e</mi><mi>x</mi></msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>−</mo><msup><mi>e</mi><mi>x</mi></msup><mo>⋅</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi></mrow><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mrow><msup><mi>e</mi><mi>x</mi></msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mrow><msup><mi>e</mi><mi>x</mi></msup><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\dfrac{e^x(x^2+1)-e^x\cdot 2x}{(x^2+1)^2}=\dfrac{e^x(x^2-2x+1)}{(x^2+1)^2}=\dfrac{e^x(x-1)^2}{(x^2+1)^2}</annotation></semantics></math><br><br>
(5) <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">[</mo><mo>sin</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mn>3</mn><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">]</mo></mrow><mn>4</mn></msup></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">y=[\sin(3x)]^4</annotation></semantics></math>：<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>4</mn><msup><mo>sin</mo><mn>3</mn></msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mn>3</mn><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>⋅</mo><mo>cos</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mn>3</mn><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>⋅</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>12</mn><msup><mo>sin</mo><mn>3</mn></msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mn>3</mn><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>cos</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mn>3</mn><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">4\sin^3(3x)\cdot\cos(3x)\cdot 3=12\sin^3(3x)\cos(3x)</annotation></semantics></math>
</div>
</div>

<div class="exercise-block">
<strong>練習 2.1</strong>　次の関数を微分せよ。<br>
(1) <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>log</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><msqrt><mrow><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msqrt><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">y=\log(x+\sqrt{x^2+1})</annotation></semantics></math> &emsp; (2) <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><msup><mi>e</mi><mrow><mo>−</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow></msup></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">y=x^2e^{-x}</annotation></semantics></math> &emsp; (3) <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow></mfrac></msqrt></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">y=\sqrt{\dfrac{1-x}{1+x}}</annotation></semantics></math> &emsp; (4) <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><msup><mo>tan</mo><mn>3</mn></msup><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">y=\tan^3 x</annotation></semantics></math>
<div class="answer-block">
(1) <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mn>1</mn><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><msqrt><mrow><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msqrt></mrow></mfrac><mo>⋅</mo><mspace width="-0.167em"></mspace><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mi>x</mi><msqrt><mrow><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msqrt></mfrac><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mrow><msqrt><mrow><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msqrt><mo>+</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow><mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><msqrt><mrow><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msqrt><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><msqrt><mrow><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msqrt></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mn>1</mn><msqrt><mrow><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msqrt></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\dfrac{1}{x+\sqrt{x^2+1}}\cdot\!\left(1+\dfrac{x}{\sqrt{x^2+1}}\right)=\dfrac{\sqrt{x^2+1}+x}{(x+\sqrt{x^2+1})\sqrt{x^2+1}}=\dfrac{1}{\sqrt{x^2+1}}</annotation></semantics></math><br><br>
(2) <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><msup><mi>e</mi><mrow><mo>−</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow></msup><mo>−</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><msup><mi>e</mi><mrow><mo>−</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow></msup><mo>=</mo><mi>x</mi><msup><mi>e</mi><mrow><mo>−</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow></msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>−</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">2xe^{-x}-x^2e^{-x}=xe^{-x}(2-x)</annotation></semantics></math><br><br>
(3) <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mspace width="-0.167em"></mspace><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mrow><mn>1</mn><mi>/</mi><mn>2</mn></mrow></msup></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">y=\!\left(\dfrac{1-x}{1+x}\right)^{1/2}</annotation></semantics></math>：<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mspace width="-0.167em"></mspace><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><mi>/</mi><mn>2</mn></mrow></msup><mo>⋅</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mrow><mo>−</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>−</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mo>−</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mn>1</mn><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup></mfrac><msqrt><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow></mfrac></msqrt><mo>=</mo><mo>−</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mn>1</mn><mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><msqrt><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow></msqrt></mrow></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\dfrac{1}{2}\!\left(\dfrac{1-x}{1+x}\right)^{-1/2}\cdot\dfrac{-(1+x)-(1-x)}{(1+x)^2}=-\dfrac{1}{(1+x)^2}\sqrt{\dfrac{1+x}{1-x}}=-\dfrac{1}{(1+x)\sqrt{1-x^2}}</annotation></semantics></math><br><br>
(4) <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>3</mn><msup><mo>tan</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mi>x</mi><mo>⋅</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mn>1</mn><mrow><msup><mo>cos</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mi>x</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mrow><mn>3</mn><msup><mo>tan</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mi>x</mi></mrow><mrow><msup><mo>cos</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mi>x</mi></mrow></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">3\tan^2 x\cdot\dfrac{1}{\cos^2 x}=\dfrac{3\tan^2 x}{\cos^2 x}</annotation></semantics></math>
</div>
</div>
</div><!-- /s2-2 -->

<!-- 2.3 -->

<div class="section" id="s2-3">
<h3>2.3 逆三角関数の微分・対数微分法</h3>

<div class="proof-box">
<strong><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mo>arctan</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mi>′</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mn>1</mn><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">(\arctan x)&#39;=\dfrac{1}{1+x^2}</annotation></semantics></math> の証明（逆関数の微分）：</strong><br>
<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>arctan</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">y=\arctan x</annotation></semantics></math> とおくと <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>tan</mo><mi>y</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">x=\tan y</annotation></semantics></math>，<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mrow><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>d</mi><mi>y</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mn>1</mn><mrow><msup><mo>cos</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mi>y</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><msup><mo>tan</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\dfrac{dx}{dy}=\dfrac{1}{\cos^2 y}=1+\tan^2 y=1+x^2</annotation></semantics></math>。逆関数の微分定理より：
<math display="block" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>y</mi><mi>′</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>d</mi><mi>y</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mrow><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi><mi>/</mi><mi>d</mi><mi>y</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
y&#39;=\frac{dy}{dx}=\frac{1}{dx/dy}=\frac{1}{1+x^2}
</annotation></semantics></math>
<div class="qed">■</div>
</div>

<div class="proof-box">
<strong><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mo>arcsin</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mi>′</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mn>1</mn><msqrt><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow></msqrt></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">(\arcsin x)&#39;=\dfrac{1}{\sqrt{1-x^2}}</annotation></semantics></math> の証明：</strong><br>
<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>arcsin</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">y=\arcsin x</annotation></semantics></math>，<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>sin</mo><mi>y</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">x=\sin y</annotation></semantics></math> より <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mrow><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>d</mi><mi>y</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mo>cos</mo><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><msup><mo>sin</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mi>y</mi></mrow></msqrt><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow></msqrt></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\dfrac{dx}{dy}=\cos y=\sqrt{1-\sin^2 y}=\sqrt{1-x^2}</annotation></semantics></math>（<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">|</mo><mi>y</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">|</mo></mrow><mo>≤</mo><mfrac><mi>π</mi><mn>2</mn></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">|y|\leq\frac{\pi}{2}</annotation></semantics></math> で <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>cos</mo><mi>y</mi><mo>≥</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\cos y\geq 0</annotation></semantics></math>）：
<math display="block" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>y</mi><mi>′</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><msqrt><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow></msqrt></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
y&#39;=\frac{1}{\sqrt{1-x^2}}
</annotation></semantics></math>
<div class="qed">■</div>
</div>

<div class="formula-box theorem">
<strong>対数微分法</strong>（複雑な積・冪 <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>f</mi><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mrow><mi>g</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow></msup></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">f(x)^{g(x)}</annotation></semantics></math> 型に有効）<br>
<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">y=f(x)</annotation></semantics></math> に対し両辺の絶対値の対数を取り，<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mi>x</mi><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">x</annotation></semantics></math> で微分する：
<math display="block" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>log</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">|</mo><mi>y</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">|</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mo>log</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">|</mo><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">|</mo></mrow><mo>⇒</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>y</mi><mi>′</mi></mrow><mi>y</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi>d</mi><mrow><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>log</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">|</mo><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">|</mo></mrow><mo>⇒</mo><mi>y</mi><mi>′</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>y</mi><mo>⋅</mo><mfrac><mi>d</mi><mrow><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>log</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">|</mo><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">|</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
\log|y|=\log|f(x)|\Rightarrow\frac{y&#39;}{y}=\frac{d}{dx}\log|f(x)|\Rightarrow y&#39;=y\cdot\frac{d}{dx}\log|f(x)|
</annotation></semantics></math>
特に <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mi>x</mi></msup></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">y=x^x</annotation></semantics></math> のような「底も指数も変数」の形では<strong>必須</strong>。
</div>

<div class="example-box">
<strong>例題 2.2</strong> <span class="lv lv-m">標準</span>　次の関数を微分せよ。<br>
(1) <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mrow><mo>sin</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow></msup></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">y=x^{\sin x}</annotation></semantics></math>（<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>&gt;</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">x&gt;0</annotation></semantics></math>）&emsp; (2) <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mrow><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mn>3</mn></msup><msqrt><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></msqrt></mrow><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>3</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">y=\dfrac{(x+1)^3\sqrt{x+2}}{(x+3)^2}</annotation></semantics></math>（<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>&gt;</mo><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">x&gt;-1</annotation></semantics></math>）
<div class="answer-block">
(1) <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>log</mo><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>sin</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>log</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\log y=\sin x\log x</annotation></semantics></math>。両辺を <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mi>x</mi><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">x</annotation></semantics></math> で微分：<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mrow><mi>y</mi><mi>′</mi></mrow><mi>y</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mo>cos</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>log</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mrow><mo>sin</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow><mi>x</mi></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\dfrac{y&#39;}{y}=\cos x\log x+\dfrac{\sin x}{x}</annotation></semantics></math><br>
<math display="block" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>y</mi><mi>′</mi><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mrow><mo>sin</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow></msup><mspace width="-0.167em"></mspace><mspace width="-0.167em"></mspace><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mo>cos</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>log</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mrow><mo>sin</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow><mi>x</mi></mfrac><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
y&#39;=x^{\sin x}\!\!\left(\cos x\log x+\frac{\sin x}{x}\right)
</annotation></semantics></math>
(2) <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>log</mo><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>log</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>+</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>log</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>log</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>3</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\log y=3\log(x+1)+\dfrac{1}{2}\log(x+2)-2\log(x+3)</annotation></semantics></math><br>
<math display="block" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mfrac><mrow><mi>y</mi><mi>′</mi></mrow><mi>y</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>3</mn><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfrac><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mrow><mn>2</mn><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow></mfrac><mo>−</mo><mfrac><mn>2</mn><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
\frac{y&#39;}{y}=\frac{3}{x+1}+\frac{1}{2(x+2)}-\frac{2}{x+3}
</annotation></semantics></math>
<math display="block" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>y</mi><mi>′</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mn>3</mn></msup><msqrt><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></msqrt></mrow><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>3</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup></mfrac><mspace width="-0.167em"></mspace><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mfrac><mn>3</mn><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfrac><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mrow><mn>2</mn><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow></mfrac><mo>−</mo><mfrac><mn>2</mn><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow></mfrac><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
y&#39;=\frac{(x+1)^3\sqrt{x+2}}{(x+3)^2}\!\left(\frac{3}{x+1}+\frac{1}{2(x+2)}-\frac{2}{x+3}\right)
</annotation></semantics></math>
</div>
</div>

<div class="exercise-block">
<strong>練習 2.2</strong><br>
(1) <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mrow><mo>tan</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow></msup></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">y=(1+x^2)^{\tan x}</annotation></semantics></math> を対数微分法で求めよ。&emsp; (2) <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mo>sin</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mrow><mo>cos</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow></msup></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">y=(\sin x)^{\cos x}</annotation></semantics></math>（<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>0</mn><mo>&lt;</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>&lt;</mo><mi>π</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">0&lt;x&lt;\pi</annotation></semantics></math>）を微分せよ。
<div class="answer-block">
(1) <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>log</mo><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>tan</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>log</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\log y=\tan x\log(1+x^2)</annotation></semantics></math>。<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mrow><mi>y</mi><mi>′</mi></mrow><mi>y</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mrow><mo>log</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><mrow><msup><mo>cos</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mi>x</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>+</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>tan</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\dfrac{y&#39;}{y}=\dfrac{\log(1+x^2)}{\cos^2 x}+\dfrac{2x\tan x}{1+x^2}</annotation></semantics></math><br>
<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>y</mi><mi>′</mi><mo>=</mo><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mrow><mo>tan</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow></msup><mspace width="-0.167em"></mspace><mspace width="-0.167em"></mspace><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mrow><mo>log</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><mrow><msup><mo>cos</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mi>x</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>+</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>tan</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow></mfrac><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">y&#39;=(1+x^2)^{\tan x}\!\!\left(\dfrac{\log(1+x^2)}{\cos^2 x}+\dfrac{2x\tan x}{1+x^2}\right)</annotation></semantics></math><br><br>
(2) <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>log</mo><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>cos</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>log</mo><mo>sin</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\log y=\cos x\log\sin x</annotation></semantics></math>。<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mrow><mi>y</mi><mi>′</mi></mrow><mi>y</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mo>−</mo><mo>sin</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>log</mo><mo>sin</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mrow><msup><mo>cos</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mi>x</mi></mrow><mrow><mo>sin</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\dfrac{y&#39;}{y}=-\sin x\log\sin x+\dfrac{\cos^2 x}{\sin x}</annotation></semantics></math><br>
<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>y</mi><mi>′</mi><mo>=</mo><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mo>sin</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mrow><mo>cos</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow></msup><mspace width="-0.167em"></mspace><mspace width="-0.167em"></mspace><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mo>−</mo><mo>sin</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>log</mo><mo>sin</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mrow><msup><mo>cos</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mi>x</mi></mrow><mrow><mo>sin</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">y&#39;=(\sin x)^{\cos x}\!\!\left(-\sin x\log\sin x+\dfrac{\cos^2 x}{\sin x}\right)</annotation></semantics></math>
</div>
</div>
</div><!-- /s2-3 -->

<!-- 2.4 -->

<div class="section" id="s2-4">
<h3>2.4 高次導関数・ライプニッツの公式</h3>

<div class="formula-box theorem">
<strong>高次導関数の公式</strong>
<math display="block" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mo>sin</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>n</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></msup><mo>=</mo><mo>sin</mo><mspace width="-0.167em"></mspace><mspace width="-0.167em"></mspace><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>n</mi><mi>π</mi></mrow><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>,</mo><mspace width="1.0em"></mspace><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mo>cos</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>n</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></msup><mo>=</mo><mo>cos</mo><mspace width="-0.167em"></mspace><mspace width="-0.167em"></mspace><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>n</mi><mi>π</mi></mrow><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>,</mo><mspace width="1.0em"></mspace><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><msup><mi>e</mi><mrow><mi>a</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow></msup><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>n</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></msup><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>a</mi><mi>n</mi></msup><msup><mi>e</mi><mrow><mi>a</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow></msup></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
(\sin x)^{(n)}=\sin\!\!\left(x+\frac{n\pi}{2}\right),\quad(\cos x)^{(n)}=\cos\!\!\left(x+\frac{n\pi}{2}\right),\quad(e^{ax})^{(n)}=a^n e^{ax}
</annotation></semantics></math>
<math display="block" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mi>x</mi></mfrac><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>n</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></msup><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mi>n</mi></msup><mi>n</mi><mi>!</mi></mrow><msup><mi>x</mi><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup></mfrac><mo>,</mo><mspace width="1.0em"></mspace><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mo>log</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>n</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></msup><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>n</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mi>!</mi></mrow><msup><mi>x</mi><mi>n</mi></msup></mfrac><mspace width="0.222em"></mspace><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>n</mi><mo>≥</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
\left(\frac{1}{x}\right)^{(n)}=\frac{(-1)^n n!}{x^{n+1}},\quad(\log x)^{(n)}=\frac{(-1)^{n-1}(n-1)!}{x^n}\ (n\geq 1)
</annotation></semantics></math>
</div>

<div class="proof-box">
<strong><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mo>sin</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>n</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></msup><mo>=</mo><mo>sin</mo><mspace width="-0.167em"></mspace><mspace width="-0.167em"></mspace><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mrow><mi>n</mi><mi>π</mi></mrow><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">(\sin x)^{(n)}=\sin\!\!\left(x+\dfrac{n\pi}{2}\right)</annotation></semantics></math> の証明（数学的帰納法）：</strong><br>
<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">n=1</annotation></semantics></math>：<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mo>sin</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mi>′</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>cos</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>sin</mo><mspace width="-0.167em"></mspace><mspace width="-0.167em"></mspace><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mi>π</mi><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">(\sin x)&#39;=\cos x=\sin\!\!\left(x+\frac{\pi}{2}\right)</annotation></semantics></math> ✓<br>
<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>k</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">n=k</annotation></semantics></math> で成立と仮定。<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>k</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">n=k+1</annotation></semantics></math>：
<math display="block" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mfrac><mi>d</mi><mrow><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>sin</mo><mspace width="-0.167em"></mspace><mspace width="-0.167em"></mspace><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>k</mi><mi>π</mi></mrow><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mo>cos</mo><mspace width="-0.167em"></mspace><mspace width="-0.167em"></mspace><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>k</mi><mi>π</mi></mrow><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mo>sin</mo><mspace width="-0.167em"></mspace><mspace width="-0.167em"></mspace><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>k</mi><mi>π</mi></mrow><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mi>π</mi><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mo>sin</mo><mspace width="-0.167em"></mspace><mspace width="-0.167em"></mspace><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>k</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mi>π</mi></mrow><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mspace width="0.222em"></mspace><mi>✓</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
\frac{d}{dx}\sin\!\!\left(x+\frac{k\pi}{2}\right)=\cos\!\!\left(x+\frac{k\pi}{2}\right)=\sin\!\!\left(x+\frac{k\pi}{2}+\frac{\pi}{2}\right)=\sin\!\!\left(x+\frac{(k+1)\pi}{2}\right)\ \checkmark
</annotation></semantics></math>
<div class="qed">■</div>
</div>

<div class="formula-box theorem">
<strong>ライプニッツの公式</strong>（積の <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mi>n</mi><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">n</annotation></semantics></math> 次導関数）
<math display="block" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo stretchy="false" form="prefix">{</mo><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mi>g</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><msup><mo stretchy="false" form="postfix">}</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>n</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></msup><mo>=</mo><munderover><mo>∑</mo><mrow><mi>k</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><mi>n</mi></munderover><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mfrac linethickness="0"><mi>n</mi><mi>k</mi></mfrac><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><msup><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>k</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><msup><mi>g</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>n</mi><mo>−</mo><mi>k</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
\{f(x)g(x)\}^{(n)}=\sum_{k=0}^{n}\binom{n}{k}f^{(k)}(x)\,g^{(n-k)}(x)
</annotation></semantics></math>
</div>

<div class="proof-box">
<strong>ライプニッツの公式の証明（数学的帰納法）：</strong><br>
<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">n=1</annotation></semantics></math>：積の微分則より <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>f</mi><mi>g</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mi>′</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>f</mi><mi>′</mi><mi>g</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>f</mi><mi>g</mi><mi>′</mi><mo>=</mo><msubsup><mo>∑</mo><mrow><mi>k</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><mn>1</mn></msubsup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mfrac linethickness="0"><mn>1</mn><mi>k</mi></mfrac><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><msup><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>k</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></msup><msup><mi>g</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mi>k</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></msup></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">(fg)&#39;=f&#39;g+fg&#39;=\sum_{k=0}^1\binom{1}{k}f^{(k)}g^{(1-k)}</annotation></semantics></math> ✓<br>
<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>m</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">n=m</annotation></semantics></math> で成立と仮定。<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>m</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">n=m+1</annotation></semantics></math>：<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>f</mi><mi>g</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>m</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></msup><mo>=</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">[</mo><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>f</mi><mi>g</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>m</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></msup><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">]</mo></mrow><mi>′</mi><mo>=</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">[</mo><msubsup><mo>∑</mo><mrow><mi>k</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><mi>m</mi></msubsup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mfrac linethickness="0"><mi>m</mi><mi>k</mi></mfrac><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><msup><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>k</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></msup><msup><mi>g</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>m</mi><mo>−</mo><mi>k</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></msup><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">]</mo></mrow><mi>′</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">(fg)^{(m+1)}=\left[(fg)^{(m)}\right]&#39;=\left[\sum_{k=0}^m\binom{m}{k}f^{(k)}g^{(m-k)}\right]&#39;</annotation></semantics></math><br>
<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>=</mo><msubsup><mo>∑</mo><mrow><mi>k</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><mi>m</mi></msubsup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mfrac linethickness="0"><mi>m</mi><mi>k</mi></mfrac><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mspace width="-0.167em"></mspace><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">[</mo><msup><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>k</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></msup><msup><mi>g</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>m</mi><mo>−</mo><mi>k</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>k</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></msup><msup><mi>g</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>m</mi><mo>−</mo><mi>k</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></msup><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">]</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">=\sum_{k=0}^m\binom{m}{k}\!\left[f^{(k+1)}g^{(m-k)}+f^{(k)}g^{(m-k+1)}\right]</annotation></semantics></math><br>
添字を整理（<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mfrac linethickness="0"><mi>m</mi><mrow><mi>k</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfrac><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>+</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mfrac linethickness="0"><mi>m</mi><mi>k</mi></mfrac><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mfrac linethickness="0"><mrow><mi>m</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mi>k</mi></mfrac><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\binom{m}{k-1}+\binom{m}{k}=\binom{m+1}{k}</annotation></semantics></math> を使う）すると <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msubsup><mo>∑</mo><mrow><mi>k</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><mrow><mi>m</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msubsup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mfrac linethickness="0"><mrow><mi>m</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mi>k</mi></mfrac><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><msup><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>k</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></msup><msup><mi>g</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>m</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mi>k</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></msup></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\sum_{k=0}^{m+1}\binom{m+1}{k}f^{(k)}g^{(m+1-k)}</annotation></semantics></math> となる ✓
<div class="qed">■</div>
</div>

<div class="example-box">
<strong>例題 2.3</strong> <span class="lv lv-a">応用</span>　次の <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mi>n</mi><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">n</annotation></semantics></math> 次導関数を求めよ。<br>
(1) <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><msup><mi>e</mi><mi>x</mi></msup><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>n</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></msup><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">(xe^x)^{(n)}</annotation></semantics></math> &emsp; (2) <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><msup><mi>e</mi><mi>x</mi></msup><mo>sin</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>n</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></msup><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">(e^x\sin x)^{(n)}</annotation></semantics></math>
<div class="answer-block">
(1) <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>f</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">f=x</annotation></semantics></math>，<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>g</mi><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>e</mi><mi>x</mi></msup></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">g=e^x</annotation></semantics></math>（<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msup><mi>g</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>k</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></msup><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>e</mi><mi>x</mi></msup></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">g^{(k)}=e^x</annotation></semantics></math>）として：
<math display="block" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mfrac linethickness="0"><mi>n</mi><mn>0</mn></mfrac><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mi>x</mi><msup><mi>e</mi><mi>x</mi></msup><mo>+</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mfrac linethickness="0"><mi>n</mi><mn>1</mn></mfrac><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>⋅</mo><msup><mi>e</mi><mi>x</mi></msup><mo>=</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>n</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><msup><mi>e</mi><mi>x</mi></msup></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
\binom{n}{0}x e^x+\binom{n}{1}1\cdot e^x=(x+n)e^x
</annotation></semantics></math>
(2) まず <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msup><mi>e</mi><mi>x</mi></msup><mo>sin</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mtext mathvariant="normal">Im</mtext><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><msup><mi>e</mi><mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><mi>i</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mi>x</mi></mrow></msup><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">e^x\sin x=\text{Im}(e^{(1+i)x})</annotation></semantics></math> とみるか，繰り返し微分：<br>
<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><msup><mi>e</mi><mi>x</mi></msup><mo>sin</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mi>′</mi><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>e</mi><mi>x</mi></msup><mo>sin</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>e</mi><mi>x</mi></msup><mo>cos</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>e</mi><mi>x</mi></msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mo>sin</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mo>cos</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mn>2</mn></msqrt><msup><mi>e</mi><mi>x</mi></msup><mo>sin</mo><mspace width="-0.167em"></mspace><mspace width="-0.167em"></mspace><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mi>π</mi><mn>4</mn></mfrac><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">(e^x\sin x)&#39;=e^x\sin x+e^x\cos x=e^x(\sin x+\cos x)=\sqrt{2}e^x\sin\!\!\left(x+\frac{\pi}{4}\right)</annotation></semantics></math><br>
帰納的に <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><msup><mi>e</mi><mi>x</mi></msup><mo>sin</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>n</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></msup><mo>=</mo><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><msqrt><mn>2</mn></msqrt><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mi>n</mi></msup><msup><mi>e</mi><mi>x</mi></msup><mo>sin</mo><mspace width="-0.167em"></mspace><mspace width="-0.167em"></mspace><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mrow><mi>n</mi><mi>π</mi></mrow><mn>4</mn></mfrac><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">(e^x\sin x)^{(n)}=(\sqrt{2})^n e^x\sin\!\!\left(x+\dfrac{n\pi}{4}\right)</annotation></semantics></math>
</div>
</div>
</div><!-- /s2-4 -->

<!-- 2.5 -->

<div class="section" id="s2-5">
<h3>2.5 増減・極値・グラフの概形</h3>

<div class="formula-box theorem">
<strong>増減・極値・凹凸の判定</strong>
<div class="table-wrap"><table>
  <tr><th>条件</th><th>意味</th></tr>
  <tr><td><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>f</mi><mi>′</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>&gt;</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">f&#39;(x)&gt;0</annotation></semantics></math> の区間</td><td>単調増加</td></tr>
  <tr><td><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>f</mi><mi>′</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>&lt;</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">f&#39;(x)&lt;0</annotation></semantics></math> の区間</td><td>単調減少</td></tr>
  <tr><td><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>f</mi><mi>′</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>a</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">f&#39;(a)=0</annotation></semantics></math> で前後符号変化あり</td><td><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>a</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">f(a)</annotation></semantics></math> は極値</td></tr>
  <tr><td><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>f</mi><mi>′</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>a</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">f&#39;(a)=0</annotation></semantics></math>，<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>f</mi><mi>″</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>a</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>&gt;</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">f&#39;&#39;(a)&gt;0</annotation></semantics></math></td><td><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>a</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">f(a)</annotation></semantics></math> は極小</td></tr>
  <tr><td><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>f</mi><mi>′</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>a</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">f&#39;(a)=0</annotation></semantics></math>，<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>f</mi><mi>″</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>a</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>&lt;</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">f&#39;&#39;(a)&lt;0</annotation></semantics></math></td><td><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>a</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">f(a)</annotation></semantics></math> は極大</td></tr>
  <tr><td><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>f</mi><mi>″</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>&gt;</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">f&#39;&#39;(x)&gt;0</annotation></semantics></math> の区間</td><td>下に凸（凹関数）</td></tr>
  <tr><td><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>f</mi><mi>″</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">f&#39;&#39;(x)=0</annotation></semantics></math> で <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>f</mi><mi>″</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">f&#39;&#39;</annotation></semantics></math> の符号変化あり</td><td>変曲点</td></tr>
</table></div>
</div>

<div class="important-box">
<strong><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>f</mi><mi>″</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>a</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">f&#39;&#39;(a)=0</annotation></semantics></math> は変曲点の必要条件であり十分条件ではない。</strong><br>
反例：<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>4</mn></msup></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">f(x)=x^4</annotation></semantics></math> では <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>f</mi><mi>″</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mn>0</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">f&#39;&#39;(0)=0</annotation></semantics></math> だが <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">x=0</annotation></semantics></math> は変曲点ではない（<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>f</mi><mi>″</mi><mo>≥</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">f&#39;&#39;\geq 0</annotation></semantics></math> は符号変化なし）。
</div>

<div class="example-box">
<strong>例題 2.4</strong> <span class="lv lv-m">標準</span>　<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mi>x</mi><msup><mi>e</mi><mrow><mo>−</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow></msup></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">f(x)=xe^{-x}</annotation></semantics></math> の増減・極値・変曲点・漸近線を調べ，概形を描け。
<div class="answer-block">
<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>f</mi><mi>′</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>e</mi><mrow><mo>−</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow></msup><mo>−</mo><mi>x</mi><msup><mi>e</mi><mrow><mo>−</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow></msup><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>e</mi><mrow><mo>−</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow></msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">f&#39;(x)=e^{-x}-xe^{-x}=e^{-x}(1-x)</annotation></semantics></math>，<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>f</mi><mi>″</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mo>−</mo><msup><mi>e</mi><mrow><mo>−</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow></msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>e</mi><mrow><mo>−</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow></msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>e</mi><mrow><mo>−</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow></msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">f&#39;&#39;(x)=-e^{-x}(1-x)+e^{-x}(-1)=e^{-x}(x-2)</annotation></semantics></math>
<div class="table-wrap"><table>
  <tr><th><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mi>x</mi><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">x</annotation></semantics></math></th><th><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mi>⋯</mi><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\cdots</annotation></semantics></math></th><th><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mn>1</mn><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">1</annotation></semantics></math></th><th><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mi>⋯</mi><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\cdots</annotation></semantics></math></th><th><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mn>2</mn><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">2</annotation></semantics></math></th><th><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mi>⋯</mi><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\cdots</annotation></semantics></math></th></tr>
  <tr><td><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>f</mi><mi>′</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">f&#39;</annotation></semantics></math></td><td><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mo>+</mo><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">+</annotation></semantics></math></td><td><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mn>0</mn><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">0</annotation></semantics></math></td><td><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mo>−</mo><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">-</annotation></semantics></math></td><td><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mo>−</mo><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">-</annotation></semantics></math></td><td><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mo>−</mo><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">-</annotation></semantics></math></td></tr>
  <tr><td><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>f</mi><mi>″</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">f&#39;&#39;</annotation></semantics></math></td><td><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mo>−</mo><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">-</annotation></semantics></math></td><td><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mo>−</mo><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">-</annotation></semantics></math></td><td><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mo>−</mo><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">-</annotation></semantics></math></td><td><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mn>0</mn><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">0</annotation></semantics></math></td><td><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mo>+</mo><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">+</annotation></semantics></math></td></tr>
  <tr><td><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mi>f</mi><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">f</annotation></semantics></math></td><td>↗ 上凸</td><td>極大 <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><msup><mi>e</mi><mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">e^{-1}</annotation></semantics></math></td><td>↘ 上凸</td><td>変曲点 <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>2</mn><msup><mi>e</mi><mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></msup></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">2e^{-2}</annotation></semantics></math></td><td>↘ 下凸</td></tr>
</table></div>
<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>→</mo><mo>−</mo><mi>∞</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">x\to-\infty</annotation></semantics></math>：<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>f</mi><mo>→</mo><mo>−</mo><mi>∞</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">f\to-\infty</annotation></semantics></math>，<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>→</mo><mo>+</mo><mi>∞</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">x\to+\infty</annotation></semantics></math>：<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>f</mi><mo>→</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">f\to 0</annotation></semantics></math>（漸近線：<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">y=0</annotation></semantics></math>）
</div>
</div>

<div class="example-box">
<strong>例題 2.5</strong> <span class="lv lv-a">応用</span>　方程式 <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msup><mi>e</mi><mi>x</mi></msup><mo>=</mo><mi>a</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">e^x=ax</annotation></semantics></math> の実数解の個数を定数 <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mi>a</mi><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">a</annotation></semantics></math> で分類せよ。
<div class="answer-block">
<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>≠</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">x\neq 0</annotation></semantics></math> のとき <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mfrac displaystyle="true"><msup><mi>e</mi><mi>x</mi></msup><mi>x</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mi>a</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\dfrac{e^x}{x}=a</annotation></semantics></math> と変形。<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>g</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><msup><mi>e</mi><mi>x</mi></msup><mi>x</mi></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">g(x)=\dfrac{e^x}{x}</annotation></semantics></math> を調べる。<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>g</mi><mi>′</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mrow><msup><mi>e</mi><mi>x</mi></msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">g&#39;(x)=\dfrac{e^x(x-1)}{x^2}</annotation></semantics></math><br><br>
<strong><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>&gt;</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">x&gt;0</annotation></semantics></math> の範囲：</strong><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">x=1</annotation></semantics></math> で最小値 <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>g</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mi>e</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">g(1)=e</annotation></semantics></math>。<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>→</mo><msup><mn>0</mn><mo>+</mo></msup></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">x\to 0^+</annotation></semantics></math>：<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>→</mo><mo>+</mo><mi>∞</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\to+\infty</annotation></semantics></math>，<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>→</mo><mo>+</mo><mi>∞</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">x\to+\infty</annotation></semantics></math>：<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>→</mo><mo>+</mo><mi>∞</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\to+\infty</annotation></semantics></math><br>
<strong><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>&lt;</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">x&lt;0</annotation></semantics></math> の範囲：</strong>常に <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>g</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>&lt;</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">g(x)&lt;0</annotation></semantics></math>，単調減少，<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>→</mo><msup><mn>0</mn><mo>−</mo></msup></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">x\to 0^-</annotation></semantics></math>：<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>→</mo><mo>−</mo><mi>∞</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\to-\infty</annotation></semantics></math>，<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>→</mo><mo>−</mo><mi>∞</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">x\to-\infty</annotation></semantics></math>：<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>→</mo><msup><mn>0</mn><mo>−</mo></msup></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\to 0^-</annotation></semantics></math><br>
<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">x=0</annotation></semantics></math> は <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msup><mi>e</mi><mn>0</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">e^0=0</annotation></semantics></math> となり不成立。
