<!-- 2.6 -->

<div class="section" id="s2-6">
<h3>2.6 平均値の定理・不等式証明</h3>

<div class="formula-box theorem">
<strong>ロールの定理・平均値の定理（MVT）</strong><br>
<strong>ロールの定理：</strong><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mi>f</mi><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">f</annotation></semantics></math> が <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">[</mo><mi>a</mi><mo>,</mo><mi>b</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">]</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">[a,b]</annotation></semantics></math> で連続，<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>a</mi><mo>,</mo><mi>b</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">(a,b)</annotation></semantics></math> で微分可能，<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>a</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>b</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">f(a)=f(b)</annotation></semantics></math> ならば <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>f</mi><mi>′</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>c</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">f&#39;(c)=0</annotation></semantics></math> となる <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>c</mi><mo>∈</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>a</mi><mo>,</mo><mi>b</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">c\in(a,b)</annotation></semantics></math> が存在する。<br><br>
<strong>平均値の定理：</strong><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mi>f</mi><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">f</annotation></semantics></math> が <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">[</mo><mi>a</mi><mo>,</mo><mi>b</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">]</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">[a,b]</annotation></semantics></math> で連続，<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>a</mi><mo>,</mo><mi>b</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">(a,b)</annotation></semantics></math> で微分可能ならば：
<math display="block" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mfrac><mrow><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>b</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>−</mo><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>a</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><mrow><mi>b</mi><mo>−</mo><mi>a</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mi>f</mi><mi>′</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>c</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mrow><mspace width="0.333em"></mspace><mtext mathvariant="normal"> となる </mtext><mspace width="0.333em"></mspace></mrow><mi>c</mi><mo>∈</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>a</mi><mo>,</mo><mi>b</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mrow><mspace width="0.333em"></mspace><mtext mathvariant="normal"> が存在する</mtext></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
\frac{f(b)-f(a)}{b-a}=f&#39;(c)\text{ となる } c\in(a,b)\text{ が存在する}
</annotation></semantics></math>
</div>

<div class="proof-box">
<strong>平均値の定理の証明：</strong><br>
<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>F</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>−</mo><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>a</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>−</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mrow><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>b</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>−</mo><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>a</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><mrow><mi>b</mi><mo>−</mo><mi>a</mi></mrow></mfrac><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>−</mo><mi>a</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">F(x)=f(x)-f(a)-\dfrac{f(b)-f(a)}{b-a}(x-a)</annotation></semantics></math> とおくと <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mi>F</mi><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">F</annotation></semantics></math> は <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">[</mo><mi>a</mi><mo>,</mo><mi>b</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">]</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">[a,b]</annotation></semantics></math> で連続，<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>a</mi><mo>,</mo><mi>b</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">(a,b)</annotation></semantics></math> で微分可能，かつ <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>F</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>a</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mi>F</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>b</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">F(a)=F(b)=0</annotation></semantics></math>。<br>
ロールの定理より <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>F</mi><mi>′</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>c</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">F&#39;(c)=0</annotation></semantics></math> となる <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>c</mi><mo>∈</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>a</mi><mo>,</mo><mi>b</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">c\in(a,b)</annotation></semantics></math> が存在する。<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>F</mi><mi>′</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mi>f</mi><mi>′</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>−</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mrow><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>b</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>−</mo><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>a</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><mrow><mi>b</mi><mo>−</mo><mi>a</mi></mrow></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">F&#39;(x)=f&#39;(x)-\dfrac{f(b)-f(a)}{b-a}</annotation></semantics></math> なので <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>f</mi><mi>′</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>c</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mrow><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>b</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>−</mo><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>a</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><mrow><mi>b</mi><mo>−</mo><mi>a</mi></mrow></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">f&#39;(c)=\dfrac{f(b)-f(a)}{b-a}</annotation></semantics></math>。
<div class="qed">■</div>
</div>

<div class="example-box">
<strong>例題 2.6</strong> <span class="lv lv-a">応用</span>　次の不等式を証明せよ。<br>
(1) <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>&gt;</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">x&gt;0</annotation></semantics></math> のとき <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msup><mi>e</mi><mi>x</mi></msup><mo>&gt;</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">e^x&gt;1+x</annotation></semantics></math> &emsp; (2) <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>&gt;</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">x&gt;0</annotation></semantics></math> のとき <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>log</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>≤</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\log x\leq x-1</annotation></semantics></math>
<div class="answer-block">
(1) <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>h</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>e</mi><mi>x</mi></msup><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">h(x)=e^x-1-x</annotation></semantics></math> とおく。<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>h</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mn>0</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">h(0)=0</annotation></semantics></math>，<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>h</mi><mi>′</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>e</mi><mi>x</mi></msup><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>&gt;</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">h&#39;(x)=e^x-1&gt;0</annotation></semantics></math>（<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>&gt;</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">x&gt;0</annotation></semantics></math>）より <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mi>h</mi><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">h</annotation></semantics></math> は単調増加。<br>
<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>∴</mo><mi>h</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>&gt;</mo><mi>h</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mn>0</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\therefore h(x)&gt;h(0)=0</annotation></semantics></math>，すなわち <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msup><mi>e</mi><mi>x</mi></msup><mo>&gt;</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">e^x&gt;1+x</annotation></semantics></math>。■<br><br>
(2) <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>h</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>−</mo><mo>log</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">h(x)=(x-1)-\log x</annotation></semantics></math> とおく。<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>h</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">h(1)=0</annotation></semantics></math>，<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>h</mi><mi>′</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mn>1</mn><mi>x</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mi>x</mi></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">h&#39;(x)=1-\dfrac{1}{x}=\dfrac{x-1}{x}</annotation></semantics></math>。<br>
<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>0</mn><mo>&lt;</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>&lt;</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">0&lt;x&lt;1</annotation></semantics></math> で <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>h</mi><mi>′</mi><mo>&lt;</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">h&#39;&lt;0</annotation></semantics></math>，<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>&gt;</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">x&gt;1</annotation></semantics></math> で <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>h</mi><mi>′</mi><mo>&gt;</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">h&#39;&gt;0</annotation></semantics></math> より <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">x=1</annotation></semantics></math> で最小値 <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>h</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">h(1)=0</annotation></semantics></math>。<br>
<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>∴</mo><mi>h</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>≥</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\therefore h(x)\geq 0</annotation></semantics></math>，すなわち <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>log</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>≤</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\log x\leq x-1</annotation></semantics></math>，等号は <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">x=1</annotation></semantics></math>。■
</div>
</div>

<div class="exam-card">
<div class="exam-hd"><span>入試問題（京大・改）</span><span class="etag tag-dif">微分</span></div>
<div class="exam-body">
<p>正の整数 <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mi>n</mi><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">n</annotation></semantics></math> に対して <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mspace width="-0.167em"></mspace><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mn>1</mn><mi>n</mi></mfrac><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mi>n</mi></msup><mo>&lt;</mo><mi>e</mi><mo>&lt;</mo><mspace width="-0.167em"></mspace><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mn>1</mn><mi>n</mi></mfrac><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\!\left(1+\dfrac{1}{n}\right)^n&lt;e&lt;\!\left(1+\dfrac{1}{n}\right)^{n+1}</annotation></semantics></math> を証明せよ。</p>
<div class="answer-block">
<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>log</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>≤</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\log x\leq x-1</annotation></semantics></math>（前問，等号は <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">x=1</annotation></semantics></math> のみ）を用いる。<br><br>
<strong>左の不等式：</strong><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mi>n</mi></mfrac><mo>&gt;</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">x=\dfrac{n+1}{n}&gt;1</annotation></semantics></math> を代入：<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>log</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mi>n</mi></mfrac><mo>&lt;</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mi>n</mi></mfrac><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>=</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mn>1</mn><mi>n</mi></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\log\dfrac{n+1}{n}&lt;\dfrac{n+1}{n}-1=\dfrac{1}{n}</annotation></semantics></math><br>
両辺 <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mi>n</mi><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">n</annotation></semantics></math> 倍：<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>log</mo><mspace width="-0.167em"></mspace><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mn>1</mn><mi>n</mi></mfrac><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>&lt;</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>=</mo><mo>log</mo><mi>e</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">n\log\!\left(1+\dfrac{1}{n}\right)&lt;1=\log e</annotation></semantics></math>，したがって <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mspace width="-0.167em"></mspace><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mn>1</mn><mi>n</mi></mfrac><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mi>n</mi></msup><mo>&lt;</mo><mi>e</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\!\left(1+\dfrac{1}{n}\right)^n&lt;e</annotation></semantics></math><br><br>
<strong>右の不等式：</strong><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mi>n</mi><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfrac><mo>&lt;</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">x=\dfrac{n}{n+1}&lt;1</annotation></semantics></math> を代入：<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>log</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mi>n</mi><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfrac><mo>&lt;</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mi>n</mi><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfrac><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>=</mo><mo>−</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mn>1</mn><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\log\dfrac{n}{n+1}&lt;\dfrac{n}{n+1}-1=-\dfrac{1}{n+1}</annotation></semantics></math><br>
つまり <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>−</mo><mo>log</mo><mspace width="-0.167em"></mspace><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mn>1</mn><mi>n</mi></mfrac><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>&lt;</mo><mo>−</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mn>1</mn><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">-\log\!\left(1+\dfrac{1}{n}\right)&lt;-\dfrac{1}{n+1}</annotation></semantics></math>，したがって <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>log</mo><mspace width="-0.167em"></mspace><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mn>1</mn><mi>n</mi></mfrac><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>&gt;</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mn>1</mn><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\log\!\left(1+\dfrac{1}{n}\right)&gt;\dfrac{1}{n+1}</annotation></semantics></math><br>
両辺 <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">n+1</annotation></semantics></math> 倍：<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>n</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>log</mo><mspace width="-0.167em"></mspace><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mn>1</mn><mi>n</mi></mfrac><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>&gt;</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>=</mo><mo>log</mo><mi>e</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">(n+1)\log\!\left(1+\dfrac{1}{n}\right)&gt;1=\log e</annotation></semantics></math>，したがって <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mspace width="-0.167em"></mspace><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mn>1</mn><mi>n</mi></mfrac><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><mo>&gt;</mo><mi>e</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\!\left(1+\dfrac{1}{n}\right)^{n+1}&gt;e</annotation></semantics></math> ■
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div><!-- /s2-6 -->

<div class="section" id="s2-7">
<h3>2.7 総合練習問題</h3>
<div class="exercise-block">
<strong>練習 2.3</strong> <span class="lv lv-a">応用</span>　<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>log</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">f(x)=x^2\log x</annotation></semantics></math>（<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>&gt;</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">x&gt;0</annotation></semantics></math>）の増減・極値・変曲点を調べよ。また <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msub><mo>lim</mo><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>→</mo><mo>+</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></msub><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\displaystyle\lim_{x\to+0}f(x)</annotation></semantics></math> を求めよ。
<div class="answer-block">
<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>f</mi><mi>′</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>log</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>x</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>log</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">f&#39;(x)=2x\log x+x=x(2\log x+1)</annotation></semantics></math>，<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>f</mi><mi>′</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>⇔</mo><mo>log</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>−</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>⇔</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>e</mi><mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><mi>/</mi><mn>2</mn></mrow></msup></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">f&#39;=0\Leftrightarrow\log x=-\frac{1}{2}\Leftrightarrow x=e^{-1/2}</annotation></semantics></math><br>
<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>0</mn><mo>&lt;</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>&lt;</mo><msup><mi>e</mi><mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><mi>/</mi><mn>2</mn></mrow></msup></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">0&lt;x&lt;e^{-1/2}</annotation></semantics></math> で <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>f</mi><mi>′</mi><mo>&lt;</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">f&#39;&lt;0</annotation></semantics></math>，<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>&gt;</mo><msup><mi>e</mi><mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><mi>/</mi><mn>2</mn></mrow></msup></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">x&gt;e^{-1/2}</annotation></semantics></math> で <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>f</mi><mi>′</mi><mo>&gt;</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">f&#39;&gt;0</annotation></semantics></math>。<strong>極小値：</strong><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><msup><mi>e</mi><mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><mi>/</mi><mn>2</mn></mrow></msup><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>e</mi><mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><mo>⋅</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mo>−</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mo>−</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mn>1</mn><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>e</mi></mrow></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">f(e^{-1/2})=e^{-1}\cdot(-\frac{1}{2})=-\dfrac{1}{2e}</annotation></semantics></math><br><br>
<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>f</mi><mi>″</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>log</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">f&#39;&#39;(x)=2\log x+3</annotation></semantics></math>，<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>f</mi><mi>″</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>⇔</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>e</mi><mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>3</mn><mi>/</mi><mn>2</mn></mrow></msup></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">f&#39;&#39;=0\Leftrightarrow x=e^{-3/2}</annotation></semantics></math>，前後で符号変化。<strong>変曲点：</strong><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><msup><mi>e</mi><mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>3</mn><mi>/</mi><mn>2</mn></mrow></msup><mo>,</mo><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mo>−</mo><mfrac><mn>3</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><msup><mi>e</mi><mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow></msup><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">(e^{-3/2},\,-\frac{3}{2}e^{-3})</annotation></semantics></math><br><br>
<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msub><mo>lim</mo><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>→</mo><mo>+</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></msub><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>log</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><msub><mo>lim</mo><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>→</mo><mo>+</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></msub><mfrac><mrow><mo>log</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow><msup><mi>x</mi><mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></msup></mfrac><mo>=</mo><msub><mo>lim</mo><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>→</mo><mo>+</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></msub><mfrac><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mi>x</mi></mfrac><mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow></msup></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mo>−</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><msub><mo>lim</mo><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>→</mo><mo>+</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></msub><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\displaystyle\lim_{x\to+0}x^2\log x=\lim_{x\to+0}\frac{\log x}{x^{-2}}=\lim_{x\to+0}\frac{\frac{1}{x}}{-2x^{-3}}=-\frac{1}{2}\lim_{x\to+0}x^2=0</annotation></semantics></math>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div><!-- /ch2 -->

