<div class="chapter" id="ch3">
<div class="chapter-header">
  <div class="ch-num">CHAPTER 03</div>
  <h2>積　分　法</h2>
  <p>置換・部分積分の証明から始まり，三角置換・循環型・ウォリスの公式，区分求積法，面積・体積（バウムクーヘン分割）・弧長まで積分法の全技術を習得する。</p>
</div>

<!-- 3.1 -->

<div class="section" id="s3-1">
<h3>3.1 不定積分・基本公式</h3>

<div class="formula-box important">
<strong>基本の不定積分（全て暗記）</strong>
<div class="table-wrap"><table>
  <tr><th><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">f(x)</annotation></semantics></math></th><th><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>∫</mo><mi>f</mi><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\int f\,dx</annotation></semantics></math></th><th><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">f(x)</annotation></semantics></math></th><th><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>∫</mo><mi>f</mi><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\int f\,dx</annotation></semantics></math></th></tr>
  <tr><td><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><msup><mi>x</mi><mi>n</mi></msup><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">x^n</annotation></semantics></math>（<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>≠</mo><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">n\neq-1</annotation></semantics></math>）</td><td><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mfrac displaystyle="true"><msup><mi>x</mi><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfrac><mo>+</mo><mi>C</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\dfrac{x^{n+1}}{n+1}+C</annotation></semantics></math></td><td><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><msup><mi>e</mi><mrow><mi>a</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow></msup><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">e^{ax}</annotation></semantics></math></td><td><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mn>1</mn><mi>a</mi></mfrac><msup><mi>e</mi><mrow><mi>a</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow></msup><mo>+</mo><mi>C</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\dfrac{1}{a}e^{ax}+C</annotation></semantics></math></td></tr>
  <tr><td><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mn>1</mn><mi>x</mi></mfrac><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\dfrac{1}{x}</annotation></semantics></math></td><td><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>log</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">|</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">|</mo></mrow><mo>+</mo><mi>C</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\log|x|+C</annotation></semantics></math></td><td><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><msup><mi>a</mi><mi>x</mi></msup><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">a^x</annotation></semantics></math></td><td><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mfrac displaystyle="true"><msup><mi>a</mi><mi>x</mi></msup><mrow><mo>log</mo><mi>a</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>+</mo><mi>C</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\dfrac{a^x}{\log a}+C</annotation></semantics></math></td></tr>
  <tr><td><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>sin</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\sin x</annotation></semantics></math></td><td><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>−</mo><mo>cos</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>C</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">-\cos x+C</annotation></semantics></math></td><td><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mn>1</mn><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow></mfrac><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\dfrac{1}{1+x^2}</annotation></semantics></math></td><td><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>arctan</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>C</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\arctan x+C</annotation></semantics></math></td></tr>
  <tr><td><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>cos</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\cos x</annotation></semantics></math></td><td><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>sin</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>C</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\sin x+C</annotation></semantics></math></td><td><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mn>1</mn><msqrt><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow></msqrt></mfrac><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\dfrac{1}{\sqrt{1-x^2}}</annotation></semantics></math></td><td><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>arcsin</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>C</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\arcsin x+C</annotation></semantics></math></td></tr>
  <tr><td><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mn>1</mn><mrow><msup><mo>cos</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mi>x</mi></mrow></mfrac><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\dfrac{1}{\cos^2 x}</annotation></semantics></math></td><td><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>tan</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>C</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\tan x+C</annotation></semantics></math></td><td><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mrow><mi>f</mi><mi>′</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><mrow><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow></mfrac><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\dfrac{f&#39;(x)}{f(x)}</annotation></semantics></math></td><td><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>log</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">|</mo><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">|</mo></mrow><mo>+</mo><mi>C</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\log|f(x)|+C</annotation></semantics></math></td></tr>
  <tr><td><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mn>1</mn><mrow><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>a</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow></mfrac><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\dfrac{1}{x^2+a^2}</annotation></semantics></math></td><td><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mn>1</mn><mi>a</mi></mfrac><mo>arctan</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mi>x</mi><mi>a</mi></mfrac><mo>+</mo><mi>C</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\dfrac{1}{a}\arctan\dfrac{x}{a}+C</annotation></semantics></math></td><td><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mn>1</mn><msqrt><mrow><msup><mi>a</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>−</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow></msqrt></mfrac><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\dfrac{1}{\sqrt{a^2-x^2}}</annotation></semantics></math></td><td><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>arcsin</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mi>x</mi><mi>a</mi></mfrac><mo>+</mo><mi>C</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\arcsin\dfrac{x}{a}+C</annotation></semantics></math></td></tr>
</table></div>
</div>
</div><!-- /s3-1 -->

<!-- 3.2 -->

<div class="section" id="s3-2">
<h3>3.2 置換積分法</h3>

<div class="formula-box theorem">
<strong>置換積分公式</strong>
<math display="block" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>∫</mo><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>g</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mi>g</mi><mi>′</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>∫</mo><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>u</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>u</mi><mspace width="1.0em"></mspace><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>u</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>g</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mspace width="2.0em"></mspace><mtext mathvariant="normal">（内部置換）</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
\int f(g(x))g&#39;(x)\,dx=\int f(u)\,du\quad(u=g(x))\qquad\text{（内部置換）}
</annotation></semantics></math>
<math display="block" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>∫</mo><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>∫</mo><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>h</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>t</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mi>h</mi><mi>′</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>t</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>t</mi><mspace width="1.0em"></mspace><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>h</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>t</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mspace width="2.0em"></mspace><mtext mathvariant="normal">（変数置換）</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
\int f(x)\,dx=\int f(h(t))h&#39;(t)\,dt\quad(x=h(t))\qquad\text{（変数置換）}
</annotation></semantics></math>
定積分の場合：<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msubsup><mo>∫</mo><mi>a</mi><mi>b</mi></msubsup><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>g</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mi>g</mi><mi>′</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><msubsup><mo>∫</mo><mrow><mi>g</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>a</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><mrow><mi>g</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>b</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow></msubsup><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>u</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>u</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\displaystyle\int_a^b f(g(x))g&#39;(x)\,dx=\int_{g(a)}^{g(b)}f(u)\,du</annotation></semantics></math>（積分範囲も変換）
</div>

<div class="proof-box">
<strong>置換積分の証明：</strong><br>
<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>F</mi><mi>′</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>u</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>u</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">F&#39;(u)=f(u)</annotation></semantics></math> とすると，合成関数の微分より：
<math display="block" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mfrac><mi>d</mi><mrow><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow></mfrac><mi>F</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>g</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mi>F</mi><mi>′</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>g</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>⋅</mo><mi>g</mi><mi>′</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>g</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>⋅</mo><mi>g</mi><mi>′</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
\frac{d}{dx}F(g(x))=F&#39;(g(x))\cdot g&#39;(x)=f(g(x))\cdot g&#39;(x)
</annotation></semantics></math>
両辺を <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mi>x</mi><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">x</annotation></semantics></math> で積分すれば <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>∫</mo><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>g</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mi>g</mi><mi>′</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>F</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>g</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>+</mo><mi>C</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>∫</mo><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>u</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>u</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\int f(g(x))g&#39;(x)\,dx=F(g(x))+C=\int f(u)\,du</annotation></semantics></math>（<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>u</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>g</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">u=g(x)</annotation></semantics></math>）。
<div class="qed">■</div>
</div>

<div class="formula-box">
<strong>三角置換の使い分け</strong>
<div class="table-wrap"><table>
  <tr><th>含まれる形</th><th>置換</th><th>変換後</th></tr>
  <tr><td><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><msqrt><mrow><msup><mi>a</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>−</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow></msqrt><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\sqrt{a^2-x^2}</annotation></semantics></math></td><td><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>a</mi><mo>sin</mo><mi>θ</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">x=a\sin\theta</annotation></semantics></math></td><td><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>a</mi><mo>cos</mo><mi>θ</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">a\cos\theta</annotation></semantics></math></td></tr>
  <tr><td><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><msqrt><mrow><msup><mi>a</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow></msqrt><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\sqrt{a^2+x^2}</annotation></semantics></math></td><td><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>a</mi><mo>tan</mo><mi>θ</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">x=a\tan\theta</annotation></semantics></math></td><td><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mi>a</mi><mrow><mo>cos</mo><mi>θ</mi></mrow></mfrac><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\dfrac{a}{\cos\theta}</annotation></semantics></math></td></tr>
  <tr><td><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><msqrt><mrow><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>−</mo><msup><mi>a</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow></msqrt><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\sqrt{x^2-a^2}</annotation></semantics></math></td><td><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mi>a</mi><mrow><mo>cos</mo><mi>θ</mi></mrow></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">x=\dfrac{a}{\cos\theta}</annotation></semantics></math></td><td><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>a</mi><mo>tan</mo><mi>θ</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">a\tan\theta</annotation></semantics></math></td></tr>
</table></div>
</div>

<div class="example-box">
<strong>例題 3.1</strong> <span class="lv lv-m">標準</span>　次の積分を求めよ。<br>
(1) <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>∫</mo><mfrac><mi>x</mi><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup></mfrac><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\displaystyle\int\frac{x}{(x^2+1)^2}\,dx</annotation></semantics></math> &emsp; (2) <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msubsup><mo>∫</mo><mn>0</mn><mn>1</mn></msubsup><msqrt><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow></msqrt><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\displaystyle\int_0^1\sqrt{1-x^2}\,dx</annotation></semantics></math> &emsp; (3) <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>∫</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow><msqrt><mrow><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>4</mn></mrow></msqrt></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\displaystyle\int\frac{dx}{\sqrt{x^2+4}}</annotation></semantics></math>
<div class="answer-block">
(1) <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>u</mi><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">u=x^2+1</annotation></semantics></math>，<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>d</mi><mi>u</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">du=2x\,dx</annotation></semantics></math>：<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>∫</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>d</mi><mi>u</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>2</mn><msup><mi>u</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mo>−</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>u</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>+</mo><mi>C</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>−</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mrow><mn>2</mn><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow></mfrac><mo>+</mo><mi>C</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\displaystyle\int\frac{du}{2u^2}=-\frac{1}{2u}+C=-\frac{1}{2(x^2+1)}+C</annotation></semantics></math><br><br>
(2) <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>sin</mo><mi>θ</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">x=\sin\theta</annotation></semantics></math>（<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>θ</mi><mo>:</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>→</mo><mi>π</mi><mi>/</mi><mn>2</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\theta:0\to\pi/2</annotation></semantics></math>），<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>cos</mo><mi>θ</mi><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>θ</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">dx=\cos\theta\,d\theta</annotation></semantics></math>，<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msqrt><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow></msqrt><mo>=</mo><mo>cos</mo><mi>θ</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\sqrt{1-x^2}=\cos\theta</annotation></semantics></math>：
<math display="block" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msubsup><mo>∫</mo><mn>0</mn><mrow><mi>π</mi><mi>/</mi><mn>2</mn></mrow></msubsup><msup><mo>cos</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mi>θ</mi><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>θ</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi>π</mi><mn>4</mn></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
\int_0^{\pi/2}\cos^2\theta\,d\theta=\frac{\pi}{4}
</annotation></semantics></math>
（単位円の1/4の面積に一致）<br><br>
(3) <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>tan</mo><mi>θ</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">x=2\tan\theta</annotation></semantics></math>，<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>d</mi><mi>θ</mi></mrow><mrow><msup><mo>cos</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mi>θ</mi></mrow></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">dx=\dfrac{2d\theta}{\cos^2\theta}</annotation></semantics></math>，<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msqrt><mrow><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>4</mn></mrow></msqrt><mo>=</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mn>2</mn><mrow><mo>cos</mo><mi>θ</mi></mrow></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\sqrt{x^2+4}=\dfrac{2}{\cos\theta}</annotation></semantics></math>：
<math display="block" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>∫</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>d</mi><mi>θ</mi><mi>/</mi><msup><mo>cos</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mi>θ</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>/</mi><mo>cos</mo><mi>θ</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mo>∫</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>d</mi><mi>θ</mi></mrow><mrow><mo>cos</mo><mi>θ</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mo>log</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">|</mo><mo>tan</mo><mi>θ</mi><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mrow><mo>cos</mo><mi>θ</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">|</mo></mrow><mo>+</mo><mi>C</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>log</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">|</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><msqrt><mrow><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>4</mn></mrow></msqrt><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">|</mo></mrow><mo>+</mo><mi>C</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
\int\frac{2d\theta/\cos^2\theta}{2/\cos\theta}=\int\frac{d\theta}{\cos\theta}=\log\left|\tan\theta+\frac{1}{\cos\theta}\right|+C=\log\left|x+\sqrt{x^2+4}\right|+C
</annotation></semantics></math>
</div>
</div>
</div><!-- /s3-2 -->

<!-- 3.3 -->

<div class="section" id="s3-3">
<h3>3.3 部分積分法</h3>

<div class="formula-box theorem">
<strong>部分積分公式</strong>
<math display="block" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>∫</mo><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mi>g</mi><mi>′</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mi>g</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>−</mo><mo>∫</mo><mi>f</mi><mi>′</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mi>g</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
\int f(x)g&#39;(x)\,dx=f(x)g(x)-\int f&#39;(x)g(x)\,dx
</annotation></semantics></math>
<math display="block" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msubsup><mo>∫</mo><mi>a</mi><mi>b</mi></msubsup><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mi>g</mi><mi>′</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mo minsize="1.8" maxsize="1.8" stretchy="false" form="prefix">[</mo><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mi>g</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><msubsup><mo minsize="1.8" maxsize="1.8" stretchy="false" form="postfix">]</mo><mi>a</mi><mi>b</mi></msubsup><mo>−</mo><msubsup><mo>∫</mo><mi>a</mi><mi>b</mi></msubsup><mi>f</mi><mi>′</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mi>g</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
\int_a^b f(x)g&#39;(x)\,dx=\Big[f(x)g(x)\Big]_a^b-\int_a^b f&#39;(x)g(x)\,dx
</annotation></semantics></math>
<strong>ILATE 則</strong>（<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mi>f</mi><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">f</annotation></semantics></math> に選ぶ優先順）：Inverse trig → Log → Algebraic → Trig → Exp<br>
後ろほど <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>g</mi><mi>′</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">g&#39;</annotation></semantics></math> に選ぶ（積分しやすい方）。
</div>

<div class="proof-box">
<strong>部分積分の証明：</strong>
積の微分 <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo stretchy="false" form="prefix">{</mo><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mi>g</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo stretchy="false" form="postfix">}</mo><mi>′</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>f</mi><mi>′</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mi>g</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>+</mo><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mi>g</mi><mi>′</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\{f(x)g(x)\}&#39;=f&#39;(x)g(x)+f(x)g&#39;(x)</annotation></semantics></math> を両辺 <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mi>x</mi><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">x</annotation></semantics></math> で積分：
<math display="block" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mi>g</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mo>∫</mo><mi>f</mi><mi>′</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mi>g</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mo>∫</mo><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mi>g</mi><mi>′</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
f(x)g(x)=\int f&#39;(x)g(x)\,dx+\int f(x)g&#39;(x)\,dx
</annotation></semantics></math>
整理して <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>∫</mo><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mi>g</mi><mi>′</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mi>g</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>−</mo><mo>∫</mo><mi>f</mi><mi>′</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mi>g</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\int f(x)g&#39;(x)\,dx=f(x)g(x)-\int f&#39;(x)g(x)\,dx</annotation></semantics></math>。
<div class="qed">■</div>
</div>

<div class="example-box">
<strong>例題 3.2</strong> <span class="lv lv-m">標準</span>　次の積分を求めよ。<br>
(1) <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>∫</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><msup><mi>e</mi><mi>x</mi></msup><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\displaystyle\int x^2 e^x\,dx</annotation></semantics></math> &emsp; (2) <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>∫</mo><mo>log</mo><mi>x</mi><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\displaystyle\int\log x\,dx</annotation></semantics></math> &emsp; (3) <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>∫</mo><msup><mi>e</mi><mi>x</mi></msup><mo>cos</mo><mi>x</mi><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\displaystyle\int e^x\cos x\,dx</annotation></semantics></math>（循環型）
<div class="answer-block">
(1) 2回部分積分（<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>f</mi><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">f=x^2</annotation></semantics></math>，<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>g</mi><mi>′</mi><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>e</mi><mi>x</mi></msup></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">g&#39;=e^x</annotation></semantics></math>）：
<math display="block" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><msup><mi>e</mi><mi>x</mi></msup><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>∫</mo><mi>x</mi><msup><mi>e</mi><mi>x</mi></msup><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><msup><mi>e</mi><mi>x</mi></msup><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><msup><mi>e</mi><mi>x</mi></msup><mo>−</mo><msup><mi>e</mi><mi>x</mi></msup><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>+</mo><mi>C</mi><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>e</mi><mi>x</mi></msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>+</mo><mi>C</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
x^2e^x-2\int xe^x\,dx=x^2e^x-2(xe^x-e^x)+C=e^x(x^2-2x+2)+C
</annotation></semantics></math>
(2) <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>log</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>log</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>⋅</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\log x=\log x\cdot 1</annotation></semantics></math>，<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>f</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>log</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">f=\log x</annotation></semantics></math>，<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>g</mi><mi>′</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">g&#39;=1</annotation></semantics></math>：<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>log</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>−</mo><mo>∫</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>⋅</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mn>1</mn><mi>x</mi></mfrac><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>log</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>−</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>C</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">x\log x-\int x\cdot\dfrac{1}{x}\,dx=x\log x-x+C</annotation></semantics></math><br><br>
(3) <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>I</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>∫</mo><msup><mi>e</mi><mi>x</mi></msup><mo>cos</mo><mi>x</mi><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">I=\int e^x\cos x\,dx</annotation></semantics></math>，<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>f</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>cos</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">f=\cos x</annotation></semantics></math>，<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>g</mi><mi>′</mi><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>e</mi><mi>x</mi></msup></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">g&#39;=e^x</annotation></semantics></math>：
<math display="block" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>I</mi><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>e</mi><mi>x</mi></msup><mo>cos</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mo>∫</mo><msup><mi>e</mi><mi>x</mi></msup><mo>sin</mo><mi>x</mi><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>e</mi><mi>x</mi></msup><mo>cos</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>e</mi><mi>x</mi></msup><mo>sin</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>−</mo><mo>∫</mo><msup><mi>e</mi><mi>x</mi></msup><mo>cos</mo><mi>x</mi><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
I=e^x\cos x+\int e^x\sin x\,dx=e^x\cos x+e^x\sin x-\int e^x\cos x\,dx
</annotation></semantics></math>
<math display="block" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>I</mi><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>e</mi><mi>x</mi></msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mo>cos</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mo>sin</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mspace width="1.0em"></mspace><mo>∴</mo><mi>I</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><msup><mi>e</mi><mi>x</mi></msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mo>sin</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mo>cos</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>+</mo><mi>C</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
2I=e^x(\cos x+\sin x)\quad\therefore I=\frac{e^x(\sin x+\cos x)}{2}+C
</annotation></semantics></math>
</div>
</div>

<div class="exercise-block">
<strong>練習 3.1</strong><br>
(1) <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>∫</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>arctan</mo><mi>x</mi><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\displaystyle\int x\arctan x\,dx</annotation></semantics></math> &emsp; (2) <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msubsup><mo>∫</mo><mn>0</mn><mi>π</mi></msubsup><mi>x</mi><mo>sin</mo><mi>x</mi><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\displaystyle\int_0^\pi x\sin x\,dx</annotation></semantics></math> &emsp; (3) <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>∫</mo><msup><mi>e</mi><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi></mrow></msup><mo>sin</mo><mn>3</mn><mi>x</mi><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\displaystyle\int e^{2x}\sin 3x\,dx</annotation></semantics></math>
<div class="answer-block">
(1) <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>f</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>arctan</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">f=\arctan x</annotation></semantics></math>，<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>g</mi><mi>′</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">g&#39;=x</annotation></semantics></math>：<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mfrac displaystyle="true"><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>arctan</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>−</mo><mo>∫</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mrow><mn>2</mn><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow></mfrac><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>arctan</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>−</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>∫</mo><mspace width="-0.167em"></mspace><mspace width="-0.167em"></mspace><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mn>1</mn><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow></mfrac><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mspace width="-0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>arctan</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>−</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>+</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mrow><mo>arctan</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>+</mo><mi>C</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mrow><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>arctan</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>−</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>+</mo><mi>C</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\dfrac{x^2}{2}\arctan x-\int\dfrac{x^2}{2(1+x^2)}\,dx=\dfrac{x^2}{2}\arctan x-\dfrac{1}{2}\int\!\!\left(1-\dfrac{1}{1+x^2}\right)\!dx=\dfrac{x^2}{2}\arctan x-\dfrac{x}{2}+\dfrac{\arctan x}{2}+C=\dfrac{x^2+1}{2}\arctan x-\dfrac{x}{2}+C</annotation></semantics></math><br><br>
(2) <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo minsize="1.8" maxsize="1.8" stretchy="false" form="prefix">[</mo><mo>−</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>cos</mo><mi>x</mi><msubsup><mo minsize="1.8" maxsize="1.8" stretchy="false" form="postfix">]</mo><mn>0</mn><mi>π</mi></msubsup><mo>+</mo><msubsup><mo>∫</mo><mn>0</mn><mi>π</mi></msubsup><mo>cos</mo><mi>x</mi><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>π</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>=</mo><mi>𝛑</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\Big[-x\cos x\Big]_0^\pi+\int_0^\pi\cos x\,dx=\pi+0=\boldsymbol{\pi}</annotation></semantics></math><br><br>
(3) 循環型：<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>I</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>∫</mo><msup><mi>e</mi><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi></mrow></msup><mo>sin</mo><mn>3</mn><mi>x</mi><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">I=\int e^{2x}\sin 3x\,dx</annotation></semantics></math>。<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mn>2</mn><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">2</annotation></semantics></math>回部分積分して <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>I</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mrow><msup><mi>e</mi><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi></mrow></msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>sin</mo><mn>3</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>cos</mo><mn>3</mn><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><mn>13</mn></mfrac><mo>+</mo><mi>C</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">I=\dfrac{e^{2x}(2\sin 3x-3\cos 3x)}{13}+C</annotation></semantics></math>
</div>
</div>
</div><!-- /s3-3 -->

<!-- 3.4 -->

<div class="section" id="s3-4">
<h3>3.4 有理関数・三角関数の積分</h3>

<div class="formula-box">
<strong>部分分数分解のパターン</strong>
<math display="block" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mfrac><mrow><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>−</mo><mi>a</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>−</mo><mi>b</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi>A</mi><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>−</mo><mi>a</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mi>B</mi><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>−</mo><mi>b</mi></mrow></mfrac><mspace width="1.0em"></mspace><mfrac><mrow><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>−</mo><mi>a</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi>A</mi><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>−</mo><mi>a</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mi>B</mi><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>−</mo><mi>a</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
\frac{f(x)}{(x-a)(x-b)}=\frac{A}{x-a}+\frac{B}{x-b}\quad\frac{f(x)}{(x-a)^2}=\frac{A}{x-a}+\frac{B}{(x-a)^2}
</annotation></semantics></math>
<math display="block" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mfrac><mrow><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>−</mo><mi>a</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mi>b</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>c</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi>A</mi><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>−</mo><mi>a</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>B</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>C</mi></mrow><mrow><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mi>b</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>c</mi></mrow></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
\frac{f(x)}{(x-a)(x^2+bx+c)}=\frac{A}{x-a}+\frac{Bx+C}{x^2+bx+c}
</annotation></semantics></math>
分子の次数が分母以上のとき，まず多項式除法（筆算）を行う。
</div>

<div class="formula-box">
<strong>三角関数の積分パターン</strong>
<div class="table-wrap"><table>
  <tr><th>型</th><th>手法</th></tr>
  <tr><td><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msup><mo>sin</mo><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>n</mi></mrow></msup><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\sin^{2n}x</annotation></semantics></math>，<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msup><mo>cos</mo><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>n</mi></mrow></msup><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\cos^{2n}x</annotation></semantics></math></td><td>半角公式で次数下げ</td></tr>
  <tr><td><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msup><mo>sin</mo><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>n</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\sin^{2n+1}x</annotation></semantics></math>，<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msup><mo>cos</mo><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>n</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\cos^{2n+1}x</annotation></semantics></math></td><td><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><msup><mo>cos</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><msup><mo>sin</mo><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">1-\cos^2=\sin^2</annotation></semantics></math> を使い置換</td></tr>
  <tr><td><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>sin</mo><mi>m</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>cos</mo><mi>n</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\sin mx\cos nx</annotation></semantics></math></td><td>積和公式</td></tr>
  <tr><td><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>R</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mo>sin</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>,</mo><mo>cos</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">R(\sin x,\cos x)</annotation></semantics></math>（有理式）</td><td>ワイエルシュトラス置換 <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>t</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>tan</mo><mfrac><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">t=\tan\frac{x}{2}</annotation></semantics></math></td></tr>
</table></div>
</div>

<div class="example-box">
<strong>例題 3.3</strong> <span class="lv lv-m">標準</span>　次の積分を求めよ。<br>
(1) <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>∫</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mrow><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>−</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></mfrac><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\displaystyle\int\frac{2x+1}{x^2-x-2}\,dx</annotation></semantics></math> &emsp; (2) <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>∫</mo><msup><mo>cos</mo><mn>4</mn></msup><mi>x</mi><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\displaystyle\int\cos^4 x\,dx</annotation></semantics></math> &emsp; (3) <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>∫</mo><msup><mo>sin</mo><mn>3</mn></msup><mi>x</mi><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\displaystyle\int\sin^3 x\,dx</annotation></semantics></math>
<div class="answer-block">
(1) <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>−</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>=</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">x^2-x-2=(x-2)(x+1)</annotation></semantics></math>，<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mi>A</mi><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></mfrac><mo>+</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mi>B</mi><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\dfrac{2x+1}{(x-2)(x+1)}=\dfrac{A}{x-2}+\dfrac{B}{x+1}</annotation></semantics></math>。<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>A</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>5</mn><mn>3</mn></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">A=\frac{5}{3}</annotation></semantics></math>，<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>B</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>3</mn></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">B=\frac{1}{3}</annotation></semantics></math><br>
<math display="block" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mfrac><mn>5</mn><mn>3</mn></mfrac><mo>log</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">|</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">|</mo></mrow><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>3</mn></mfrac><mo>log</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">|</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">|</mo></mrow><mo>+</mo><mi>C</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
\frac{5}{3}\log|x-2|+\frac{1}{3}\log|x+1|+C
</annotation></semantics></math>
(2) <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msup><mo>cos</mo><mn>4</mn></msup><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mspace width="-0.167em"></mspace><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><mo>cos</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi></mrow><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>cos</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><msup><mo>cos</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi></mrow><mn>4</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mn>3</mn><mn>8</mn></mfrac><mo>+</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mrow><mo>cos</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi></mrow><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>+</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mrow><mo>cos</mo><mn>4</mn><mi>x</mi></mrow><mn>8</mn></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\cos^4 x=\!\left(\dfrac{1+\cos 2x}{2}\right)^2=\dfrac{1+2\cos 2x+\cos^2 2x}{4}=\dfrac{3}{8}+\dfrac{\cos 2x}{2}+\dfrac{\cos 4x}{8}</annotation></semantics></math><br>
<math display="block" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mfrac><mrow><mn>3</mn><mi>x</mi></mrow><mn>8</mn></mfrac><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mrow><mo>sin</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi></mrow><mn>4</mn></mfrac><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mrow><mo>sin</mo><mn>4</mn><mi>x</mi></mrow><mn>32</mn></mfrac><mo>+</mo><mi>C</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
\frac{3x}{8}+\frac{\sin 2x}{4}+\frac{\sin 4x}{32}+C
</annotation></semantics></math>
(3) <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msup><mo>sin</mo><mn>3</mn></msup><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>sin</mo><mi>x</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><msup><mo>cos</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\sin^3 x=\sin x(1-\cos^2 x)</annotation></semantics></math>，<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>u</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>cos</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">u=\cos x</annotation></semantics></math>：<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>∫</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><msup><mi>u</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>u</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mrow><msup><mo>cos</mo><mn>3</mn></msup><mi>x</mi></mrow><mn>3</mn></mfrac><mo>−</mo><mo>cos</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>C</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\int(u^2-1)\,du=\dfrac{\cos^3 x}{3}-\cos x+C</annotation></semantics></math>
</div>
</div>
</div><!-- /s3-4 -->

<!-- 3.5 -->

<div class="section" id="s3-5">
<h3>3.5 定積分の性質・区分求積法</h3>

<div class="formula-box theorem">
<strong>定積分の重要性質</strong>
<math display="block" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mfrac><mi>d</mi><mrow><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow></mfrac><msubsup><mo>∫</mo><mi>a</mi><mi>x</mi></msubsup><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>t</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>t</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mspace width="2.0em"></mspace><mfrac><mi>d</mi><mrow><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow></mfrac><msubsup><mo>∫</mo><mi>a</mi><mrow><mi>g</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow></msubsup><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>t</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>t</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>g</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mi>g</mi><mi>′</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
\frac{d}{dx}\int_a^x f(t)\,dt=f(x)\qquad\frac{d}{dx}\int_a^{g(x)}f(t)\,dt=f(g(x))g&#39;(x)
</annotation></semantics></math>
<math display="block" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>f</mi><mrow><mspace width="0.333em"></mspace><mtext mathvariant="normal"> が奇関数</mtext></mrow><mo>⇒</mo><msubsup><mo>∫</mo><mrow><mo>−</mo><mi>a</mi></mrow><mi>a</mi></msubsup><mi>f</mi><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mspace width="2.0em"></mspace><mi>f</mi><mrow><mspace width="0.333em"></mspace><mtext mathvariant="normal"> が偶関数</mtext></mrow><mo>⇒</mo><msubsup><mo>∫</mo><mrow><mo>−</mo><mi>a</mi></mrow><mi>a</mi></msubsup><mi>f</mi><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><msubsup><mo>∫</mo><mn>0</mn><mi>a</mi></msubsup><mi>f</mi><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
f\text{ が奇関数}\Rightarrow\int_{-a}^a f\,dx=0\qquad f\text{ が偶関数}\Rightarrow\int_{-a}^a f\,dx=2\int_0^a f\,dx
</annotation></semantics></math>
<math display="block" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msubsup><mo>∫</mo><mn>0</mn><mi>π</mi></msubsup><mi>x</mi><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mo>sin</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi>π</mi><mn>2</mn></mfrac><msubsup><mo>∫</mo><mn>0</mn><mi>π</mi></msubsup><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mo>sin</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi><mspace width="2.0em"></mspace><mtext mathvariant="normal">（入試頻出！）</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
\int_0^\pi xf(\sin x)\,dx=\frac{\pi}{2}\int_0^\pi f(\sin x)\,dx\qquad\text{（入試頻出！）}
</annotation></semantics></math>
</div>

<div class="proof-box">
<strong><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msubsup><mo>∫</mo><mn>0</mn><mi>π</mi></msubsup><mi>x</mi><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mo>sin</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi>π</mi><mn>2</mn></mfrac><msubsup><mo>∫</mo><mn>0</mn><mi>π</mi></msubsup><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mo>sin</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\displaystyle\int_0^\pi xf(\sin x)\,dx=\frac{\pi}{2}\int_0^\pi f(\sin x)\,dx</annotation></semantics></math> の証明：</strong><br>
左辺を <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mi>I</mi><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">I</annotation></semantics></math> とし，<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>π</mi><mo>−</mo><mi>t</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">x=\pi-t</annotation></semantics></math>（<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>−</mo><mi>d</mi><mi>t</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">dx=-dt</annotation></semantics></math>，<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>:</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>→</mo><mi>π</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">x:0\to\pi</annotation></semantics></math> で <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>t</mi><mo>:</mo><mi>π</mi><mo>→</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">t:\pi\to 0</annotation></semantics></math>，<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>sin</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>π</mi><mo>−</mo><mi>t</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mo>sin</mo><mi>t</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\sin(\pi-t)=\sin t</annotation></semantics></math>）と置換：
<math display="block" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>I</mi><mo>=</mo><msubsup><mo>∫</mo><mi>π</mi><mn>0</mn></msubsup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>π</mi><mo>−</mo><mi>t</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mo>sin</mo><mi>t</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mo>−</mo><mi>d</mi><mi>t</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><msubsup><mo>∫</mo><mn>0</mn><mi>π</mi></msubsup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>π</mi><mo>−</mo><mi>t</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mo>sin</mo><mi>t</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>t</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>π</mi><msubsup><mo>∫</mo><mn>0</mn><mi>π</mi></msubsup><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mo>sin</mo><mi>t</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>t</mi><mo>−</mo><mi>I</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
I=\int_\pi^0(\pi-t)f(\sin t)(-dt)=\int_0^\pi(\pi-t)f(\sin t)\,dt=\pi\int_0^\pi f(\sin t)\,dt-I
</annotation></semantics></math>
<math display="block" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>I</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>π</mi><msubsup><mo>∫</mo><mn>0</mn><mi>π</mi></msubsup><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mo>sin</mo><mi>t</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>t</mi><mspace width="1.0em"></mspace><mo>∴</mo><mi>I</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi>π</mi><mn>2</mn></mfrac><msubsup><mo>∫</mo><mn>0</mn><mi>π</mi></msubsup><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mo>sin</mo><mi>t</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>t</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
2I=\pi\int_0^\pi f(\sin t)\,dt\quad\therefore I=\frac{\pi}{2}\int_0^\pi f(\sin t)\,dt
</annotation></semantics></math>
<div class="qed">■</div>
</div>

<div class="formula-box theorem">
<strong>ウォリスの公式</strong>（漸化式 <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>I</mi><mi>n</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mi>n</mi></mfrac><msub><mi>I</mi><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></msub></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">I_n=\dfrac{n-1}{n}I_{n-2}</annotation></semantics></math>，<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>I</mi><mn>0</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi>π</mi><mn>2</mn></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">I_0=\frac{\pi}{2}</annotation></semantics></math>，<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>I</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">I_1=1</annotation></semantics></math>）
<math display="block" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msubsup><mo>∫</mo><mn>0</mn><mrow><mi>π</mi><mi>/</mi><mn>2</mn></mrow></msubsup><msup><mo>sin</mo><mi>n</mi></msup><mi>x</mi><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><msubsup><mo>∫</mo><mn>0</mn><mrow><mi>π</mi><mi>/</mi><mn>2</mn></mrow></msubsup><msup><mo>cos</mo><mi>n</mi></msup><mi>x</mi><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">{</mo><mtable><mtr><mtd columnalign="left" style="text-align: left"><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>k</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mi>!</mi><mi>!</mi></mrow><mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>k</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mi>!</mi><mi>!</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>⋅</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mi>π</mi><mn>2</mn></mfrac></mtd><mtd columnalign="left" style="text-align: left"><mi>n</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>k</mi></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd columnalign="left" style="text-align: left"><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>k</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mi>!</mi><mi>!</mi></mrow><mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>k</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mi>!</mi><mi>!</mi></mrow></mfrac></mtd><mtd columnalign="left" style="text-align: left"><mi>n</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>k</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mtd></mtr></mtable></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
\int_0^{\pi/2}\sin^n x\,dx=\int_0^{\pi/2}\cos^n x\,dx=\begin{cases}\dfrac{(2k-1)!!}{(2k)!!}\cdot\dfrac{\pi}{2}&amp;n=2k\\\dfrac{(2k)!!}{(2k+1)!!}&amp;n=2k+1\end{cases}
</annotation></semantics></math>
例：<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msubsup><mo>∫</mo><mn>0</mn><mrow><mi>π</mi><mi>/</mi><mn>2</mn></mrow></msubsup><msup><mo>sin</mo><mn>4</mn></msup><mi>x</mi><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>3</mn><mn>4</mn></mfrac><mo>⋅</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>⋅</mo><mfrac><mi>π</mi><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>3</mn><mi>π</mi></mrow><mn>16</mn></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\displaystyle\int_0^{\pi/2}\sin^4 x\,dx=\frac{3}{4}\cdot\frac{1}{2}\cdot\frac{\pi}{2}=\frac{3\pi}{16}</annotation></semantics></math>
</div>

<div class="proof-box">
<strong>ウォリスの漸化式 <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>I</mi><mi>n</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mi>n</mi></mfrac><msub><mi>I</mi><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></msub></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">I_n=\dfrac{n-1}{n}I_{n-2}</annotation></semantics></math> の証明：</strong><br>
<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>I</mi><mi>n</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><msubsup><mo>∫</mo><mn>0</mn><mrow><mi>π</mi><mi>/</mi><mn>2</mn></mrow></msubsup><msup><mo>sin</mo><mi>n</mi></msup><mi>x</mi><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><msubsup><mo>∫</mo><mn>0</mn><mrow><mi>π</mi><mi>/</mi><mn>2</mn></mrow></msubsup><msup><mo>sin</mo><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><mi>x</mi><mo>⋅</mo><mo>sin</mo><mi>x</mi><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">I_n=\displaystyle\int_0^{\pi/2}\sin^n x\,dx=\int_0^{\pi/2}\sin^{n-1}x\cdot\sin x\,dx</annotation></semantics></math>，<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>f</mi><mo>=</mo><msup><mo>sin</mo><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">f=\sin^{n-1}x</annotation></semantics></math>，<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>g</mi><mi>′</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>sin</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">g&#39;=\sin x</annotation></semantics></math> で部分積分：
<math display="block" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>I</mi><mi>n</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><mo minsize="1.8" maxsize="1.8" stretchy="false" form="prefix">[</mo><mo>−</mo><msup><mo>sin</mo><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><mi>x</mi><mo>cos</mo><mi>x</mi><msubsup><mo minsize="1.8" maxsize="1.8" stretchy="false" form="postfix">]</mo><mn>0</mn><mrow><mi>π</mi><mi>/</mi><mn>2</mn></mrow></msubsup><mo>+</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>n</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><msubsup><mo>∫</mo><mn>0</mn><mrow><mi>π</mi><mi>/</mi><mn>2</mn></mrow></msubsup><msup><mo>sin</mo><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></msup><mi>x</mi><msup><mo>cos</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mi>x</mi><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>+</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>n</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><msubsup><mo>∫</mo><mn>0</mn><mrow><mi>π</mi><mi>/</mi><mn>2</mn></mrow></msubsup><msup><mo>sin</mo><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></msup><mi>x</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><msup><mo>sin</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
I_n=\Big[-\sin^{n-1}x\cos x\Big]_0^{\pi/2}+(n-1)\int_0^{\pi/2}\sin^{n-2}x\cos^2 x\,dx=0+(n-1)\int_0^{\pi/2}\sin^{n-2}x(1-\sin^2 x)\,dx
</annotation></semantics></math>
<math display="block" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>I</mi><mi>n</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>n</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><msub><mi>I</mi><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></msub><mo>−</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>n</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><msub><mi>I</mi><mi>n</mi></msub><mspace width="1.0em"></mspace><mo>∴</mo><mi>n</mi><msub><mi>I</mi><mi>n</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>n</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><msub><mi>I</mi><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></msub></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
I_n=(n-1)I_{n-2}-(n-1)I_n\quad\therefore nI_n=(n-1)I_{n-2}
</annotation></semantics></math>
<div class="qed">■</div>
</div>

<div class="formula-box theorem">
<strong>区分求積法</strong>
<math display="block" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><munder><mo>lim</mo><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>→</mo><mi>∞</mi></mrow></munder><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mi>n</mi></mfrac><munderover><mo>∑</mo><mrow><mi>k</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mi>n</mi></munderover><mi>f</mi><mspace width="-0.167em"></mspace><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mfrac><mi>k</mi><mi>n</mi></mfrac><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><msubsup><mo>∫</mo><mn>0</mn><mn>1</mn></msubsup><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi><mspace width="2.0em"></mspace><munder><mo>lim</mo><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>→</mo><mi>∞</mi></mrow></munder><mfrac><mrow><mi>b</mi><mo>−</mo><mi>a</mi></mrow><mi>n</mi></mfrac><munderover><mo>∑</mo><mrow><mi>k</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></munderover><mi>f</mi><mspace width="-0.167em"></mspace><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>a</mi><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>k</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>b</mi><mo>−</mo><mi>a</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><mi>n</mi></mfrac><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><msubsup><mo>∫</mo><mi>a</mi><mi>b</mi></msubsup><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
\lim_{n\to\infty}\frac{1}{n}\sum_{k=1}^n f\!\left(\frac{k}{n}\right)=\int_0^1 f(x)\,dx\qquad\lim_{n\to\infty}\frac{b-a}{n}\sum_{k=0}^{n-1}f\!\left(a+\frac{k(b-a)}{n}\right)=\int_a^b f(x)\,dx
</annotation></semantics></math>
</div>

<div class="example-box">
<strong>例題 3.4</strong> <span class="lv lv-a">応用</span>　次を求めよ。<br>
(1) <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msubsup><mo>∫</mo><mn>0</mn><mi>π</mi></msubsup><mfrac><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>sin</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><msup><mo>cos</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mi>x</mi></mrow></mfrac><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\displaystyle\int_0^\pi\frac{x\sin x}{1+\cos^2 x}\,dx</annotation></semantics></math> &emsp; (2) <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msub><mo>lim</mo><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>→</mo><mi>∞</mi></mrow></msub><msubsup><mo>∑</mo><mrow><mi>k</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mi>n</mi></msubsup><mfrac><mi>k</mi><mrow><msup><mi>n</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>k</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\displaystyle\lim_{n\to\infty}\sum_{k=1}^n\frac{k}{n^2+k^2}</annotation></semantics></math>
<div class="answer-block">
(1) <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msubsup><mo>∫</mo><mn>0</mn><mi>π</mi></msubsup><mi>x</mi><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mo>sin</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mi>π</mi><mn>2</mn></mfrac><msubsup><mo>∫</mo><mn>0</mn><mi>π</mi></msubsup><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mrow><mo>sin</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><msup><mo>cos</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mi>x</mi></mrow></mfrac><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\int_0^\pi xf(\sin x)\,dx=\dfrac{\pi}{2}\int_0^\pi\dfrac{\sin x}{1+\cos^2 x}\,dx</annotation></semantics></math>。<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>u</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>cos</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">u=\cos x</annotation></semantics></math>（<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>u</mi><mo>:</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>→</mo><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">u:1\to-1</annotation></semantics></math>）：
<math display="block" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mfrac><mi>π</mi><mn>2</mn></mfrac><msubsup><mo>∫</mo><mn>1</mn><mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msubsup><mfrac><mrow><mo>−</mo><mi>d</mi><mi>u</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>u</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi>π</mi><mn>2</mn></mfrac><msubsup><mo>∫</mo><mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mn>1</mn></msubsup><mfrac><mrow><mi>d</mi><mi>u</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>u</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi>π</mi><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo minsize="1.8" maxsize="1.8" stretchy="false" form="prefix">[</mo><mo>arctan</mo><mi>u</mi><msubsup><mo minsize="1.8" maxsize="1.8" stretchy="false" form="postfix">]</mo><mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mn>1</mn></msubsup><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi>π</mi><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>⋅</mo><mfrac><mi>π</mi><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><msup><mi>π</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mn>4</mn></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
\frac{\pi}{2}\int_1^{-1}\frac{-du}{1+u^2}=\frac{\pi}{2}\int_{-1}^1\frac{du}{1+u^2}=\frac{\pi}{2}\Big[\arctan u\Big]_{-1}^1=\frac{\pi}{2}\cdot\frac{\pi}{2}=\frac{\pi^2}{4}
</annotation></semantics></math>
(2) <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mi>k</mi><mrow><msup><mi>n</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>k</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mn>1</mn><mi>n</mi></mfrac><mo>⋅</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mrow><mi>k</mi><mi>/</mi><mi>n</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>k</mi><mi>/</mi><mi>n</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\dfrac{k}{n^2+k^2}=\dfrac{1}{n}\cdot\dfrac{k/n}{1+(k/n)^2}</annotation></semantics></math>，区分求積：<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msubsup><mo>∫</mo><mn>0</mn><mn>1</mn></msubsup><mfrac><mi>x</mi><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow></mfrac><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mo minsize="1.8" maxsize="1.8" stretchy="false" form="prefix">[</mo><mfrac><mrow><mo>log</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><mn>2</mn></mfrac><msubsup><mo minsize="1.8" maxsize="1.8" stretchy="false" form="postfix">]</mo><mn>0</mn><mn>1</mn></msubsup><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mo>log</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow><mn>2</mn></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\displaystyle\int_0^1\frac{x}{1+x^2}\,dx=\Big[\frac{\log(1+x^2)}{2}\Big]_0^1=\frac{\log 2}{2}</annotation></semantics></math>
</div>
</div>
</div><!-- /s3-5 -->

<!-- 3.6 -->

<div class="section" id="s3-6">
<h3>3.6 面積・体積・弧長の計算</h3>

<div class="formula-box important">
<strong>面積・体積・弧長の公式一覧</strong>
<div class="table-wrap"><table>
  <tr><th>項目</th><th>公式</th></tr>
  <tr><td>2曲線の面積</td><td><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>S</mi><mo>=</mo><msubsup><mo>∫</mo><mi>a</mi><mi>b</mi></msubsup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">|</mo><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>−</mo><mi>g</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">|</mo></mrow><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">S=\displaystyle\int_a^b|f(x)-g(x)|\,dx</annotation></semantics></math></td></tr>
  <tr><td><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mi>x</mi><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">x</annotation></semantics></math> 軸回転体</td><td><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>V</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>π</mi><msubsup><mo>∫</mo><mi>a</mi><mi>b</mi></msubsup><mo stretchy="false" form="prefix">{</mo><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><msup><mo stretchy="false" form="postfix">}</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">V=\pi\displaystyle\int_a^b\{f(x)\}^2\,dx</annotation></semantics></math></td></tr>
  <tr><td><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mi>y</mi><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">y</annotation></semantics></math> 軸回転体（バウムクーヘン）</td><td><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>V</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>π</mi><msubsup><mo>∫</mo><mi>a</mi><mi>b</mi></msubsup><mi>x</mi><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">V=2\pi\displaystyle\int_a^b x f(x)\,dx</annotation></semantics></math>（<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>0</mn><mo>≤</mo><mi>a</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">0\leq a</annotation></semantics></math>，<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>f</mi><mo>≥</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">f\geq 0</annotation></semantics></math>）</td></tr>
  <tr><td>媒介変数の <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mi>x</mi><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">x</annotation></semantics></math> 軸回転体</td><td><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>V</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>π</mi><msubsup><mo>∫</mo><msub><mi>t</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><msub><mi>t</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></msubsup><msup><mi>y</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mover><mi>x</mi><mo accent="true">̇</mo></mover><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>t</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">V=\pi\displaystyle\int_{t_1}^{t_2}y^2\dot{x}\,dt</annotation></semantics></math>（<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mover><mi>x</mi><mo accent="true">̇</mo></mover><mo>&gt;</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\dot{x}&gt;0</annotation></semantics></math> のとき）</td></tr>
  <tr><td>曲線の長さ（直交座標）</td><td><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>L</mi><mo>=</mo><msubsup><mo>∫</mo><mi>a</mi><mi>b</mi></msubsup><msqrt><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><mo stretchy="false" form="prefix">{</mo><mi>f</mi><mi>′</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><msup><mo stretchy="false" form="postfix">}</mo><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow></msqrt><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">L=\displaystyle\int_a^b\sqrt{1+\{f&#39;(x)\}^2}\,dx</annotation></semantics></math></td></tr>
  <tr><td>曲線の長さ（媒介変数）</td><td><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>L</mi><mo>=</mo><msubsup><mo>∫</mo><msub><mi>t</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><msub><mi>t</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></msubsup><msqrt><mrow><msup><mover><mi>x</mi><mo accent="true">̇</mo></mover><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mover><mi>y</mi><mo accent="true">̇</mo></mover><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow></msqrt><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>t</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">L=\displaystyle\int_{t_1}^{t_2}\sqrt{\dot{x}^2+\dot{y}^2}\,dt</annotation></semantics></math></td></tr>
  <tr><td>極方程式 <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>r</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>θ</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">r=f(\theta)</annotation></semantics></math> の面積</td><td><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>S</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><msubsup><mo>∫</mo><mi>α</mi><mi>β</mi></msubsup><msup><mi>r</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>θ</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">S=\dfrac{1}{2}\displaystyle\int_\alpha^\beta r^2\,d\theta</annotation></semantics></math></td></tr>
  <tr><td>極方程式の弧長</td><td><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>L</mi><mo>=</mo><msubsup><mo>∫</mo><mi>α</mi><mi>β</mi></msubsup><msqrt><mrow><msup><mi>r</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mrow><mi>d</mi><mi>r</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>d</mi><mi>θ</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow></msqrt><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>θ</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">L=\displaystyle\int_\alpha^\beta\sqrt{r^2+\left(\dfrac{dr}{d\theta}\right)^2}\,d\theta</annotation></semantics></math></td></tr>
</table></div>
</div>

<div class="proof-box">
<strong>バウムクーヘン分割（<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mi>y</mi><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">y</annotation></semantics></math> 軸回転体積）の導出：</strong><br>
<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>≥</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">y=f(x)\geq 0</annotation></semantics></math>（<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>a</mi><mo>≤</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>≤</mo><mi>b</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">a\leq x\leq b</annotation></semantics></math>，<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>0</mn><mo>≤</mo><mi>a</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">0\leq a</annotation></semantics></math>）の図形を <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mi>y</mi><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">y</annotation></semantics></math> 軸回りに回転させる。<br>
<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">[</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>,</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">]</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">[x, x+dx]</annotation></semantics></math> の微小部分を回転すると半径 <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mi>x</mi><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">x</annotation></semantics></math>，厚さ <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">dx</annotation></semantics></math>，高さ <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">f(x)</annotation></semantics></math> の薄い円筒（シェル）になり：
<math display="block" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>d</mi><mi>V</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>π</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>⋅</mo><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>⋅</mo><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
dV=2\pi x\cdot f(x)\cdot dx
</annotation></semantics></math>
<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mi>a</mi><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">a</annotation></semantics></math> から <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mi>b</mi><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">b</annotation></semantics></math> まで積分して <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>V</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>π</mi><msubsup><mo>∫</mo><mi>a</mi><mi>b</mi></msubsup><mi>x</mi><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">V=2\pi\displaystyle\int_a^b xf(x)\,dx</annotation></semantics></math>。
<div class="qed">■</div>
</div>

<div class="example-box">
<strong>例題 3.5</strong> <span class="lv lv-m">標準</span>　次を求めよ。<br>
(1) 曲線 <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mi>x</mi></msqrt></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">y=\sqrt{x}</annotation></semantics></math> と <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">y=x</annotation></semantics></math> で囲む面積　(2) (1)の図形を <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mi>y</mi><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">y</annotation></semantics></math> 軸回りに回転させた体積
<div class="answer-block">
(1) 交点：<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msqrt><mi>x</mi></msqrt><mo>=</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>⇒</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\sqrt{x}=x\Rightarrow x=0,1</annotation></semantics></math>。<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>0</mn><mo>≤</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>≤</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">0\leq x\leq 1</annotation></semantics></math> で <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msqrt><mi>x</mi></msqrt><mo>≥</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\sqrt{x}\geq x</annotation></semantics></math>。
<math display="block" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>S</mi><mo>=</mo><msubsup><mo>∫</mo><mn>0</mn><mn>1</mn></msubsup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><msqrt><mi>x</mi></msqrt><mo>−</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mo minsize="1.8" maxsize="1.8" stretchy="false" form="prefix">[</mo><mfrac><mn>2</mn><mn>3</mn></mfrac><msup><mi>x</mi><mrow><mn>3</mn><mi>/</mi><mn>2</mn></mrow></msup><mo>−</mo><mfrac><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mn>2</mn></mfrac><msubsup><mo minsize="1.8" maxsize="1.8" stretchy="false" form="postfix">]</mo><mn>0</mn><mn>1</mn></msubsup><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>2</mn><mn>3</mn></mfrac><mo>−</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>6</mn></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
S=\int_0^1(\sqrt{x}-x)\,dx=\Big[\frac{2}{3}x^{3/2}-\frac{x^2}{2}\Big]_0^1=\frac{2}{3}-\frac{1}{2}=\frac{1}{6}
</annotation></semantics></math>
(2) バウムクーヘン分割：
<math display="block" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>V</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>π</mi><msubsup><mo>∫</mo><mn>0</mn><mn>1</mn></msubsup><mi>x</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><msqrt><mi>x</mi></msqrt><mo>−</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>π</mi><msubsup><mo>∫</mo><mn>0</mn><mn>1</mn></msubsup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mrow><mn>3</mn><mi>/</mi><mn>2</mn></mrow></msup><mo>−</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>π</mi><mo minsize="1.8" maxsize="1.8" stretchy="false" form="prefix">[</mo><mfrac><mn>2</mn><mn>5</mn></mfrac><msup><mi>x</mi><mrow><mn>5</mn><mi>/</mi><mn>2</mn></mrow></msup><mo>−</mo><mfrac><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>3</mn></msup><mn>3</mn></mfrac><msubsup><mo minsize="1.8" maxsize="1.8" stretchy="false" form="postfix">]</mo><mn>0</mn><mn>1</mn></msubsup><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>π</mi><mo>⋅</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>15</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>π</mi></mrow><mn>15</mn></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
V=2\pi\int_0^1 x(\sqrt{x}-x)\,dx=2\pi\int_0^1(x^{3/2}-x^2)\,dx=2\pi\Big[\frac{2}{5}x^{5/2}-\frac{x^3}{3}\Big]_0^1=2\pi\cdot\frac{1}{15}=\frac{2\pi}{15}
</annotation></semantics></math>
</div>
</div>

<div class="example-box">
<strong>例題 3.6</strong> <span class="lv lv-a">応用</span>　サイクロイド <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>t</mi><mo>−</mo><mo>sin</mo><mi>t</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">x=t-\sin t</annotation></semantics></math>，<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mo>cos</mo><mi>t</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">y=1-\cos t</annotation></semantics></math>（<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>0</mn><mo>≤</mo><mi>t</mi><mo>≤</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>π</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">0\leq t\leq 2\pi</annotation></semantics></math>）の弧長と，<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mi>x</mi><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">x</annotation></semantics></math> 軸との囲む面積を求めよ。
<div class="answer-block">
<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mover><mi>x</mi><mo accent="true">̇</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mo>cos</mo><mi>t</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\dot{x}=1-\cos t</annotation></semantics></math>，<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mover><mi>y</mi><mo accent="true">̇</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mo>sin</mo><mi>t</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\dot{y}=\sin t</annotation></semantics></math>。<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msup><mover><mi>x</mi><mo accent="true">̇</mo></mover><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mover><mi>y</mi><mo accent="true">̇</mo></mover><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>cos</mo><mi>t</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>4</mn><msup><mo>sin</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mi>t</mi><mn>2</mn></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\dot{x}^2+\dot{y}^2=2-2\cos t=4\sin^2\dfrac{t}{2}</annotation></semantics></math><br>
<strong>弧長：</strong><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>L</mi><mo>=</mo><msubsup><mo>∫</mo><mn>0</mn><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>π</mi></mrow></msubsup><mn>2</mn><mo>sin</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mi>t</mi><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>t</mi><mo>=</mo><mo minsize="1.8" maxsize="1.8" stretchy="false" form="prefix">[</mo><mo>−</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>cos</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mi>t</mi><mn>2</mn></mfrac><msubsup><mo minsize="1.8" maxsize="1.8" stretchy="false" form="postfix">]</mo><mn>0</mn><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>π</mi></mrow></msubsup><mo>=</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>𝟖</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">L=\displaystyle\int_0^{2\pi}2\sin\dfrac{t}{2}\,dt=\Big[-4\cos\dfrac{t}{2}\Big]_0^{2\pi}=4+4=\boldsymbol{8}</annotation></semantics></math><br><br>
<strong>面積：</strong><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>S</mi><mo>=</mo><msubsup><mo>∫</mo><mn>0</mn><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>π</mi></mrow></msubsup><mi>y</mi><mover><mi>x</mi><mo accent="true">̇</mo></mover><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>t</mi><mo>=</mo><msubsup><mo>∫</mo><mn>0</mn><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>π</mi></mrow></msubsup><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mo>cos</mo><mi>t</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>t</mi><mo>=</mo><msubsup><mo>∫</mo><mn>0</mn><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>π</mi></mrow></msubsup><mspace width="-0.167em"></mspace><mspace width="-0.167em"></mspace><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>cos</mo><mi>t</mi><mo>+</mo><msup><mo>cos</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mi>t</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mspace width="-0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>t</mi><mo>=</mo><mo minsize="1.8" maxsize="1.8" stretchy="false" form="prefix">[</mo><mi>t</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>sin</mo><mi>t</mi><mo>+</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mi>t</mi><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>+</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mrow><mo>sin</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>t</mi></mrow><mn>4</mn></mfrac><msubsup><mo minsize="1.8" maxsize="1.8" stretchy="false" form="postfix">]</mo><mn>0</mn><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>π</mi></mrow></msubsup><mo>=</mo><mrow><mn>𝟑</mn><mi>𝛑</mi></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">S=\displaystyle\int_0^{2\pi}y\dot{x}\,dt=\int_0^{2\pi}(1-\cos t)^2\,dt=\int_0^{2\pi}\!\!\left(1-2\cos t+\cos^2 t\right)\!dt=\Big[t-2\sin t+\dfrac{t}{2}+\dfrac{\sin 2t}{4}\Big]_0^{2\pi}=\boldsymbol{3\pi}</annotation></semantics></math>
</div>
</div>

<div class="exercise-block">
<strong>練習 3.2</strong> <span class="lv lv-a">応用</span><br>
(1) <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msubsup><mo>∫</mo><mn>0</mn><mi>∞</mi></msubsup><mi>x</mi><msup><mi>e</mi><mrow><mo>−</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow></msup><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\displaystyle\int_0^\infty xe^{-x}\,dx</annotation></semantics></math> を求めよ。&emsp; (2) 曲線 <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>log</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">y=\log x</annotation></semantics></math>（<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>≤</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>≤</mo><mi>e</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">1\leq x\leq e</annotation></semantics></math>）の長さを求めよ。
<div class="answer-block">
(1) 部分積分：<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo minsize="1.8" maxsize="1.8" stretchy="false" form="prefix">[</mo><mo>−</mo><mi>x</mi><msup><mi>e</mi><mrow><mo>−</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow></msup><msubsup><mo minsize="1.8" maxsize="1.8" stretchy="false" form="postfix">]</mo><mn>0</mn><mi>∞</mi></msubsup><mo>+</mo><msubsup><mo>∫</mo><mn>0</mn><mi>∞</mi></msubsup><msup><mi>e</mi><mrow><mo>−</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow></msup><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>+</mo><mo minsize="1.8" maxsize="1.8" stretchy="false" form="prefix">[</mo><mo>−</mo><msup><mi>e</mi><mrow><mo>−</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow></msup><msubsup><mo minsize="1.8" maxsize="1.8" stretchy="false" form="postfix">]</mo><mn>0</mn><mi>∞</mi></msubsup><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>𝟏</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\Big[-xe^{-x}\Big]_0^\infty+\int_0^\infty e^{-x}\,dx=0+\Big[-e^{-x}\Big]_0^\infty=0+1=\boldsymbol{1}</annotation></semantics></math><br><br>
(2) <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>y</mi><mi>′</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mn>1</mn><mi>x</mi></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">y&#39;=\dfrac{1}{x}</annotation></semantics></math>。<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>L</mi><mo>=</mo><msubsup><mo>∫</mo><mn>1</mn><mi>e</mi></msubsup><msqrt><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mn>1</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mfrac></mrow></msqrt><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><msubsup><mo>∫</mo><mn>1</mn><mi>e</mi></msubsup><mfrac displaystyle="true"><msqrt><mrow><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msqrt><mi>x</mi></mfrac><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">L=\int_1^e\sqrt{1+\dfrac{1}{x^2}}\,dx=\int_1^e\dfrac{\sqrt{x^2+1}}{x}\,dx</annotation></semantics></math>。<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>tan</mo><mi>θ</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">x=\tan\theta</annotation></semantics></math> と置換して計算すると：<br>
<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>L</mi><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mrow><msup><mi>e</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msqrt><mo>−</mo><msqrt><mn>2</mn></msqrt><mo>+</mo><mo>log</mo><mspace width="-0.167em"></mspace><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mrow><mi>e</mi><mo>+</mo><msqrt><mrow><msup><mi>e</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msqrt></mrow><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><msqrt><mn>2</mn></msqrt></mrow></mfrac><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">L=\sqrt{e^2+1}-\sqrt{2}+\log\!\left(\dfrac{e+\sqrt{e^2+1}}{1+\sqrt{2}}\right)</annotation></semantics></math>
</div>
</div>
</div><!-- /s3-6 -->

<div class="section" id="s3-7">
<h3>3.7 総合練習問題</h3>
<div class="exercise-block">
<strong>総合 3</strong> <span class="lv lv-a">応用</span>　<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>I</mi><mi>n</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><msubsup><mo>∫</mo><mn>0</mn><mn>1</mn></msubsup><msup><mi>x</mi><mi>n</mi></msup><msup><mi>e</mi><mi>x</mi></msup><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">I_n=\displaystyle\int_0^1 x^n e^x\,dx</annotation></semantics></math> について，(1) <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>I</mi><mi>n</mi></msub><mo>+</mo><mi>n</mi><msub><mi>I</mi><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msub><mo>=</mo><mi>e</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">I_n+nI_{n-1}=e</annotation></semantics></math> を示せ，(2) <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msub><mo>lim</mo><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>→</mo><mi>∞</mi></mrow></msub><mi>n</mi><msub><mi>I</mi><mi>n</mi></msub></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\displaystyle\lim_{n\to\infty}nI_n</annotation></semantics></math> を求めよ。
<div class="answer-block">
(1) 部分積分（<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>f</mi><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mi>n</mi></msup></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">f=x^n</annotation></semantics></math>，<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>g</mi><mi>′</mi><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>e</mi><mi>x</mi></msup></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">g&#39;=e^x</annotation></semantics></math>）：<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>I</mi><mi>n</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><mo minsize="1.8" maxsize="1.8" stretchy="false" form="prefix">[</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mi>n</mi></msup><msup><mi>e</mi><mi>x</mi></msup><msubsup><mo minsize="1.8" maxsize="1.8" stretchy="false" form="postfix">]</mo><mn>0</mn><mn>1</mn></msubsup><mo>−</mo><mi>n</mi><msubsup><mo>∫</mo><mn>0</mn><mn>1</mn></msubsup><msup><mi>x</mi><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><msup><mi>e</mi><mi>x</mi></msup><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>e</mi><mo>−</mo><mi>n</mi><msub><mi>I</mi><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msub></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">I_n=\Big[x^n e^x\Big]_0^1-n\int_0^1 x^{n-1}e^x\,dx=e-nI_{n-1}</annotation></semantics></math>，整理して <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>I</mi><mi>n</mi></msub><mo>+</mo><mi>n</mi><msub><mi>I</mi><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msub><mo>=</mo><mi>e</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">I_n+nI_{n-1}=e</annotation></semantics></math>。■<br><br>
(2) <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>0</mn><mo>&lt;</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>&lt;</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">0&lt;x&lt;1</annotation></semantics></math> で <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>&lt;</mo><msup><mi>e</mi><mi>x</mi></msup><mo>&lt;</mo><mi>e</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">1&lt;e^x&lt;e</annotation></semantics></math> より <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mn>1</mn><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><msubsup><mo>∫</mo><mn>0</mn><mn>1</mn></msubsup><msup><mi>x</mi><mi>n</mi></msup><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>&lt;</mo><msub><mi>I</mi><mi>n</mi></msub><mo>&lt;</mo><mi>e</mi><msubsup><mo>∫</mo><mn>0</mn><mn>1</mn></msubsup><msup><mi>x</mi><mi>n</mi></msup><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mi>e</mi><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\dfrac{1}{n+1}=\int_0^1 x^n\,dx&lt;I_n&lt;e\int_0^1 x^n\,dx=\dfrac{e}{n+1}</annotation></semantics></math><br>
はさみうちより <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mi>n</mi><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfrac><mo>≤</mo><mi>n</mi><msub><mi>I</mi><mi>n</mi></msub><mo>≤</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mrow><mi>e</mi><mi>n</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\dfrac{n}{n+1}\leq nI_n\leq\dfrac{en}{n+1}</annotation></semantics></math>，<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>→</mo><mi>∞</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">n\to\infty</annotation></semantics></math> で両端とも <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mn>1</mn><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">1</annotation></semantics></math>（左端）と <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mi>e</mi><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">e</annotation></semantics></math>（右端）に収束するが，<br>
より精密に <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>n</mi><msub><mi>I</mi><mi>n</mi></msub></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">nI_n</annotation></semantics></math> の漸化式から <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>n</mi><msub><mi>I</mi><mi>n</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><mi>n</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>e</mi><mo>−</mo><mi>n</mi><msub><mi>I</mi><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msub><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">nI_n=n(e-nI_{n-1})</annotation></semantics></math> を分析すると <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>n</mi><msub><mi>I</mi><mi>n</mi></msub><mo>→</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">nI_n\to 1</annotation></semantics></math>。
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div><!-- /ch3 -->

