     第４章　ベクトル
============================================================ -->

<div class="chapter" id="ch4">
<div class="chapter-header">
  <div class="ch-num">CHAPTER 04</div>
  <h2>ベ ク ト ル</h2>
  <p>ベクトルの代数的演算から始まり，内積の幾何学的意味，空間の直線・平面の方程式，外積（クロス積）による体積計算まで体系的に学ぶ。</p>
</div>

<!-- 4.1 -->

<div class="section" id="s4-1">
<h3>4.1 ベクトルの演算・分点公式</h3>

<div class="formula-box important">
<strong>基本公式（平面・空間共通）</strong>
<math display="block" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mover><mi>a</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>±</mo><mover><mi>b</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><msub><mi>a</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>±</mo><msub><mi>b</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>,</mo><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><msub><mi>a</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>±</mo><msub><mi>b</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>,</mo><mspace width="0.167em"></mspace><msub><mi>a</mi><mn>3</mn></msub><mo>±</mo><msub><mi>b</mi><mn>3</mn></msub><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>,</mo><mspace width="1.0em"></mspace><mi>k</mi><mover><mi>a</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>k</mi><msub><mi>a</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>,</mo><mi>k</mi><msub><mi>a</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>,</mo><mi>k</mi><msub><mi>a</mi><mn>3</mn></msub><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
\vec{a}\pm\vec{b}=(a_1\pm b_1,\,a_2\pm b_2,\,a_3\pm b_3),\quad k\vec{a}=(ka_1,ka_2,ka_3)
</annotation></semantics></math>
<math display="block" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">|</mo><mover><mi>a</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">|</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mrow><msubsup><mi>a</mi><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></msubsup><mo>+</mo><msubsup><mi>a</mi><mn>2</mn><mn>2</mn></msubsup><mo>+</mo><msubsup><mi>a</mi><mn>3</mn><mn>2</mn></msubsup></mrow></msqrt></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
|\vec{a}|=\sqrt{a_1^2+a_2^2+a_3^2}
</annotation></semantics></math>
<strong>分点公式：</strong><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>A</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mover><mi>a</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">A(\vec{a})</annotation></semantics></math>，<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>B</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mover><mi>b</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">B(\vec{b})</annotation></semantics></math> を <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>m</mi><mo>:</mo><mi>n</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">m:n</annotation></semantics></math> に内分する点 <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mi>P</mi><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">P</annotation></semantics></math> の位置ベクトル：
<math display="block" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mover><mi>p</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>n</mi><mover><mi>a</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>+</mo><mi>m</mi><mover><mi>b</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover></mrow><mrow><mi>m</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>n</mi></mrow></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
\vec{p}=\frac{n\vec{a}+m\vec{b}}{m+n}
</annotation></semantics></math>
外分（<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>m</mi><mo>:</mo><mi>n</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">m:n</annotation></semantics></math>，<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>m</mi><mo>≠</mo><mi>n</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">m\neq n</annotation></semantics></math>）：<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mover><mi>p</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mrow><mo>−</mo><mi>n</mi><mover><mi>a</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>+</mo><mi>m</mi><mover><mi>b</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover></mrow><mrow><mi>m</mi><mo>−</mo><mi>n</mi></mrow></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\vec{p}=\dfrac{-n\vec{a}+m\vec{b}}{m-n}</annotation></semantics></math>　　重心：<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mover><mi>g</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mrow><mover><mi>a</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>+</mo><mover><mi>b</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>+</mo><mover><mi>c</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover></mrow><mn>3</mn></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\vec{g}=\dfrac{\vec{a}+\vec{b}+\vec{c}}{3}</annotation></semantics></math>
</div>

<div class="formula-box theorem">
<strong>一次独立と表現の一意性</strong><br>
2ベクトル <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mover><mi>a</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\vec{a}</annotation></semantics></math>，<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mover><mi>b</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\vec{b}</annotation></semantics></math> が<strong>一次独立</strong>（平行でない，<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mover><mn>0</mn><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\vec{0}</annotation></semantics></math> でない）のとき，平面上の任意の <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mover><mi>p</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\vec{p}</annotation></semantics></math> は <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mover><mi>p</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mi>s</mi><mover><mi>a</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>+</mo><mi>t</mi><mover><mi>b</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\vec{p}=s\vec{a}+t\vec{b}</annotation></semantics></math> と一意に表せる。<br>
<strong>共線条件：</strong><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>A</mi><mo>,</mo><mi>P</mi><mo>,</mo><mi>B</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">A,P,B</annotation></semantics></math> が同一直線上 <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mo>⇔</mo><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\Leftrightarrow</annotation></semantics></math> <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mover><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>P</mi></mrow><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mi>k</mi><mover><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi></mrow><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\overrightarrow{AP}=k\overrightarrow{AB}</annotation></semantics></math> となる実数 <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mi>k</mi><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">k</annotation></semantics></math> が存在。
</div>

<div class="example-box">
<strong>例題 4.1</strong> <span class="lv lv-m">標準</span>　<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>△</mi><mi>O</mi><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\triangle OAB</annotation></semantics></math> において <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mover><mrow><mi>O</mi><mi>A</mi></mrow><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mover><mi>a</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\overrightarrow{OA}=\vec{a}</annotation></semantics></math>，<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mover><mrow><mi>O</mi><mi>B</mi></mrow><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mover><mi>b</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\overrightarrow{OB}=\vec{b}</annotation></semantics></math> とする。辺 <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>O</mi><mi>A</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">OA</annotation></semantics></math>，<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>O</mi><mi>B</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">OB</annotation></semantics></math> の <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>2</mn><mo>:</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">2:1</annotation></semantics></math> 内分点をそれぞれ <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mi>M</mi><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">M</annotation></semantics></math>，<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mi>N</mi><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">N</annotation></semantics></math> とし，<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>B</mi><mi>M</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">BM</annotation></semantics></math> と <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>N</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">AN</annotation></semantics></math> の交点 <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mi>P</mi><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">P</annotation></semantics></math> を求めよ。
<div class="answer-block">
<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mover><mrow><mi>O</mi><mi>M</mi></mrow><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mn>2</mn><mn>3</mn></mfrac><mover><mi>a</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\overrightarrow{OM}=\dfrac{2}{3}\vec{a}</annotation></semantics></math>，<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mover><mrow><mi>O</mi><mi>N</mi></mrow><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mn>1</mn><mn>3</mn></mfrac><mover><mi>b</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\overrightarrow{ON}=\dfrac{1}{3}\vec{b}</annotation></semantics></math><br><br>
直線 <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>B</mi><mi>M</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">BM</annotation></semantics></math> 上：<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mover><mrow><mi>O</mi><mi>P</mi></mrow><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mover><mi>b</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>+</mo><mi>t</mi><mspace width="-0.167em"></mspace><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mn>2</mn><mn>3</mn></mfrac><mover><mi>a</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>−</mo><mover><mi>b</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>t</mi></mrow><mn>3</mn></mfrac><mover><mi>a</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>+</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mi>t</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mover><mi>b</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\overrightarrow{OP}=\vec{b}+t\!\left(\dfrac{2}{3}\vec{a}-\vec{b}\right)=\dfrac{2t}{3}\vec{a}+(1-t)\vec{b}</annotation></semantics></math><br>
直線 <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>N</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">AN</annotation></semantics></math> 上：<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mover><mrow><mi>O</mi><mi>P</mi></mrow><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mover><mi>a</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>+</mo><mi>s</mi><mspace width="-0.167em"></mspace><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mn>1</mn><mn>3</mn></mfrac><mover><mi>b</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>−</mo><mover><mi>a</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mi>s</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mover><mi>a</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>+</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mi>s</mi><mn>3</mn></mfrac><mover><mi>b</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\overrightarrow{OP}=\vec{a}+s\!\left(\dfrac{1}{3}\vec{b}-\vec{a}\right)=(1-s)\vec{a}+\dfrac{s}{3}\vec{b}</annotation></semantics></math><br><br>
<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mover><mi>a</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>,</mo><mover><mi>b</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\vec{a},\vec{b}</annotation></semantics></math> は一次独立なので係数比較：<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>t</mi></mrow><mn>3</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mi>s</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\dfrac{2t}{3}=1-s</annotation></semantics></math>，<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mi>t</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mi>s</mi><mn>3</mn></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">1-t=\dfrac{s}{3}</annotation></semantics></math><br>
解くと <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>t</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mn>3</mn><mn>5</mn></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">t=\dfrac{3}{5}</annotation></semantics></math>，<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>s</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mn>6</mn><mn>5</mn></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">s=\dfrac{6}{5}</annotation></semantics></math>（<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mi>P</mi><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">P</annotation></semantics></math> は <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>N</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">AN</annotation></semantics></math> の延長上）<br>
<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mover><mrow><mi>O</mi><mi>P</mi></mrow><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mn>2</mn><mn>5</mn></mfrac><mover><mi>a</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>+</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mn>2</mn><mn>5</mn></mfrac><mover><mi>b</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\overrightarrow{OP}=\dfrac{2}{5}\vec{a}+\dfrac{2}{5}\vec{b}</annotation></semantics></math>
</div>
</div>
</div><!-- /s4-1 -->

<!-- 4.2 -->

<div class="section" id="s4-2">
<h3>4.2 内積・正射影・角度</h3>

<div class="formula-box definition">
<strong>内積の定義と成分公式</strong>
<math display="block" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mover><mi>a</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>⋅</mo><mover><mi>b</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">|</mo><mover><mi>a</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">|</mo></mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">|</mo><mover><mi>b</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">|</mo></mrow><mo>cos</mo><mi>θ</mi><mspace width="1.0em"></mspace><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>≤</mo><mi>θ</mi><mo>≤</mo><mi>π</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
\vec{a}\cdot\vec{b}=|\vec{a}||\vec{b}|\cos\theta\quad(0\leq\theta\leq\pi)
</annotation></semantics></math>
<math display="block" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mover><mi>a</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>⋅</mo><mover><mi>b</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><msub><mi>a</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><msub><mi>b</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>+</mo><msub><mi>a</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi>b</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>+</mo><msub><mi>a</mi><mn>3</mn></msub><msub><mi>b</mi><mn>3</mn></msub></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
\vec{a}\cdot\vec{b}=a_1b_1+a_2b_2+a_3b_3
</annotation></semantics></math>
</div>

<div class="proof-box">
<strong>内積の成分表示の証明：</strong><br>
余弦定理 <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">|</mo><mover><mi>a</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>−</mo><mover><mi>b</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">|</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">|</mo><mover><mi>a</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">|</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">|</mo><mover><mi>b</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">|</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">|</mo><mover><mi>a</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">|</mo></mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">|</mo><mover><mi>b</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">|</mo></mrow><mo>cos</mo><mi>θ</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">|\vec{a}-\vec{b}|^2=|\vec{a}|^2+|\vec{b}|^2-2|\vec{a}||\vec{b}|\cos\theta</annotation></semantics></math> と，成分計算 <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">|</mo><mover><mi>a</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>−</mo><mover><mi>b</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">|</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><msub><mi>a</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>−</mo><msub><mi>b</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><msub><mi>a</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>−</mo><msub><mi>b</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><msub><mi>a</mi><mn>3</mn></msub><mo>−</mo><msub><mi>b</mi><mn>3</mn></msub><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">|</mo><mover><mi>a</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">|</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">|</mo><mover><mi>b</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">|</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><msub><mi>a</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><msub><mi>b</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>+</mo><msub><mi>a</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi>b</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>+</mo><msub><mi>a</mi><mn>3</mn></msub><msub><mi>b</mi><mn>3</mn></msub><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">|\vec{a}-\vec{b}|^2=(a_1-b_1)^2+(a_2-b_2)^2+(a_3-b_3)^2=|\vec{a}|^2+|\vec{b}|^2-2(a_1b_1+a_2b_2+a_3b_3)</annotation></semantics></math> を比較して：
<math display="block" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">|</mo><mover><mi>a</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">|</mo></mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">|</mo><mover><mi>b</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">|</mo></mrow><mo>cos</mo><mi>θ</mi><mo>=</mo><msub><mi>a</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><msub><mi>b</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>+</mo><msub><mi>a</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi>b</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>+</mo><msub><mi>a</mi><mn>3</mn></msub><msub><mi>b</mi><mn>3</mn></msub></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
|\vec{a}||\vec{b}|\cos\theta=a_1b_1+a_2b_2+a_3b_3
</annotation></semantics></math>
<div class="qed">■</div>
</div>

<div class="formula-box theorem">
<strong>内積の重要公式</strong>
<math display="block" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">|</mo><mover><mi>a</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>±</mo><mover><mi>b</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">|</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">|</mo><mover><mi>a</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">|</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>±</mo><mn>2</mn><mover><mi>a</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>⋅</mo><mover><mi>b</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>+</mo><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">|</mo><mover><mi>b</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">|</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
|\vec{a}\pm\vec{b}|^2=|\vec{a}|^2\pm 2\vec{a}\cdot\vec{b}+|\vec{b}|^2
</annotation></semantics></math>
<strong>垂直条件：</strong><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mover><mi>a</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>⊥</mo><mover><mi>b</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>⇔</mo><mover><mi>a</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>⋅</mo><mover><mi>b</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\vec{a}\perp\vec{b}\Leftrightarrow\vec{a}\cdot\vec{b}=0</annotation></semantics></math>（<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mover><mi>a</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>,</mo><mover><mi>b</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>≠</mo><mover><mn>0</mn><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\vec{a},\vec{b}\neq\vec{0}</annotation></semantics></math>）<br>
<strong>正射影ベクトル：</strong><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mover><mi>b</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\vec{b}</annotation></semantics></math> の <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mover><mi>a</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\vec{a}</annotation></semantics></math> への正射影 <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>=</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mrow><mover><mi>a</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>⋅</mo><mover><mi>b</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover></mrow><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">|</mo><mover><mi>a</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">|</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup></mfrac><mover><mi>a</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">=\dfrac{\vec{a}\cdot\vec{b}}{|\vec{a}|^2}\vec{a}</annotation></semantics></math><br>
<strong>三角形の面積：</strong><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>S</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><msqrt><mrow><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">|</mo><mover><mi>b</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">|</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">|</mo><mover><mi>c</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">|</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>−</mo><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mover><mi>b</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>⋅</mo><mover><mi>c</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow></msqrt></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">S=\dfrac{1}{2}\sqrt{|\vec{b}|^2|\vec{c}|^2-(\vec{b}\cdot\vec{c})^2}</annotation></semantics></math>（<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mover><mi>b</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mover><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi></mrow><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\vec{b}=\overrightarrow{AB}</annotation></semantics></math>，<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mover><mi>c</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mover><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>C</mi></mrow><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\vec{c}=\overrightarrow{AC}</annotation></semantics></math>）
</div>

<div class="example-box">
<strong>例題 4.2</strong> <span class="lv lv-m">標準</span>　<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mover><mi>a</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>,</mo><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>3</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\vec{a}=(2,-1,3)</annotation></semantics></math>，<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mover><mi>b</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>,</mo><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\vec{b}=(1,2,-1)</annotation></semantics></math> について，(1) <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mover><mi>a</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>⋅</mo><mover><mi>b</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\vec{a}\cdot\vec{b}</annotation></semantics></math>，(2) なす角 <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mi>θ</mi><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\theta</annotation></semantics></math>，(3) <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mover><mi>b</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\vec{b}</annotation></semantics></math> を <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mover><mi>a</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\vec{a}</annotation></semantics></math> に平行な成分と垂直な成分に分解せよ。
<div class="answer-block">
(1) <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mover><mi>a</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>⋅</mo><mover><mi>b</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>−</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>=</mo><mo>−</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\vec{a}\cdot\vec{b}=2-2-3=-3</annotation></semantics></math><br><br>
(2) <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">|</mo><mover><mi>a</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">|</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mn>14</mn></msqrt></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">|\vec{a}|=\sqrt{14}</annotation></semantics></math>，<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">|</mo><mover><mi>b</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">|</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mn>6</mn></msqrt></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">|\vec{b}|=\sqrt{6}</annotation></semantics></math>。<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>cos</mo><mi>θ</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow><msqrt><mn>84</mn></msqrt></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mo>−</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mn>3</mn><mrow><mn>2</mn><msqrt><mn>21</mn></msqrt></mrow></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\cos\theta=\dfrac{-3}{\sqrt{84}}=-\dfrac{3}{2\sqrt{21}}</annotation></semantics></math><br><br>
(3) 平行成分：<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mrow><mover><mi>a</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>⋅</mo><mover><mi>b</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover></mrow><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">|</mo><mover><mi>a</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">|</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup></mfrac><mover><mi>a</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow><mn>14</mn></mfrac><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>,</mo><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>3</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mspace width="-0.167em"></mspace><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mo>−</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mn>3</mn><mn>7</mn></mfrac><mo>,</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mn>3</mn><mn>14</mn></mfrac><mo>,</mo><mo>−</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mn>9</mn><mn>14</mn></mfrac><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\dfrac{\vec{a}\cdot\vec{b}}{|\vec{a}|^2}\vec{a}=\dfrac{-3}{14}(2,-1,3)=\!\left(-\dfrac{3}{7},\dfrac{3}{14},-\dfrac{9}{14}\right)</annotation></semantics></math><br>
垂直成分：<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mover><mi>b</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>−</mo><mspace width="-0.167em"></mspace><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mo>−</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mn>3</mn><mn>7</mn></mfrac><mo>,</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mn>3</mn><mn>14</mn></mfrac><mo>,</mo><mo>−</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mn>9</mn><mn>14</mn></mfrac><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mspace width="-0.167em"></mspace><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mn>10</mn><mn>7</mn></mfrac><mo>,</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mn>25</mn><mn>14</mn></mfrac><mo>,</mo><mo>−</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mn>5</mn><mn>14</mn></mfrac><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\vec{b}-\!\left(-\dfrac{3}{7},\dfrac{3}{14},-\dfrac{9}{14}\right)=\!\left(\dfrac{10}{7},\dfrac{25}{14},-\dfrac{5}{14}\right)</annotation></semantics></math>
</div>
</div>

<div class="exercise-block">
<strong>練習 4.1</strong><br>
<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>△</mi><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\triangle ABC</annotation></semantics></math> において <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mover><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi></mrow><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>,</mo><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\overrightarrow{AB}=(1,2,-2)</annotation></semantics></math>，<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mover><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>C</mi></mrow><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>,</mo><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\overrightarrow{AC}=(2,-1,1)</annotation></semantics></math> とする。<br>
(1) <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>∠</mi><mi>A</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\angle A</annotation></semantics></math> を求めよ。&emsp; (2) <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>△</mi><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\triangle ABC</annotation></semantics></math> の面積を求めよ。&emsp; (3) <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mi>A</mi><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">A</annotation></semantics></math> から <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">BC</annotation></semantics></math> に下ろした垂線の足 <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mi>H</mi><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">H</annotation></semantics></math> を求めよ。
<div class="answer-block">
(1) <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mover><mi>b</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>⋅</mo><mover><mi>c</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>=</mo><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\vec{b}\cdot\vec{c}=2-2-2=-2</annotation></semantics></math>，<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">|</mo><mover><mi>b</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">|</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">|\vec{b}|=3</annotation></semantics></math>，<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">|</mo><mover><mi>c</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">|</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mn>6</mn></msqrt></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">|\vec{c}|=\sqrt{6}</annotation></semantics></math>。<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>cos</mo><mi>A</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow><mrow><mn>3</mn><msqrt><mn>6</mn></msqrt></mrow></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\cos A=\dfrac{-2}{3\sqrt{6}}</annotation></semantics></math><br><br>
(2) <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>S</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><msqrt><mrow><mn>9</mn><mo>⋅</mo><mn>6</mn><mo>−</mo><mn>4</mn></mrow></msqrt><mo>=</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><msqrt><mn>50</mn></msqrt><mo>=</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mrow><mn>5</mn><msqrt><mn>2</mn></msqrt></mrow><mn>2</mn></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">S=\dfrac{1}{2}\sqrt{9\cdot 6-4}=\dfrac{1}{2}\sqrt{50}=\dfrac{5\sqrt{2}}{2}</annotation></semantics></math><br><br>
(3) <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>H</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>B</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>t</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>C</mi><mo>−</mo><mi>B</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">H=B+t(C-B)</annotation></semantics></math> で <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mover><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>H</mi></mrow><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>⊥</mo><mover><mrow><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi></mrow><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\overrightarrow{AH}\perp\overrightarrow{BC}</annotation></semantics></math>：<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mover><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>H</mi></mrow><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mover><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi></mrow><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>+</mo><mi>t</mi><mover><mrow><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi></mrow><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><mi>t</mi><mo>,</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>−</mo><mn>3</mn><mi>t</mi><mo>,</mo><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>3</mn><mi>t</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\overrightarrow{AH}=\overrightarrow{AB}+t\overrightarrow{BC}=(1+t,2-3t,-2+3t)</annotation></semantics></math>，<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mover><mrow><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi></mrow><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>,</mo><mo>−</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>3</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\overrightarrow{BC}=(1,-3,3)</annotation></semantics></math>。<br>
内積 <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">=0</annotation></semantics></math>：<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><mi>t</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>3</mn><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>−</mo><mn>3</mn><mi>t</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>+</mo><mn>3</mn><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>3</mn><mi>t</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>⇒</mo><mn>19</mn><mi>t</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>11</mn><mo>⇒</mo><mi>t</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mn>11</mn><mn>19</mn></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">(1+t)-3(2-3t)+3(-2+3t)=0\Rightarrow 19t=11\Rightarrow t=\dfrac{11}{19}</annotation></semantics></math>。<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>H</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>A</mi><mo>+</mo><mover><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>H</mi></mrow><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">H=A+\overrightarrow{AH}</annotation></semantics></math>（<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mi>A</mi><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">A</annotation></semantics></math> を原点とすれば <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>H</mi><mo>=</mo><mover><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>H</mi></mrow><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">H=\overrightarrow{AH}</annotation></semantics></math> のベクトル）
</div>
</div>
</div><!-- /s4-2 -->

<!-- 4.3 -->

<div class="section" id="s4-3">
<h3>4.3 空間ベクトルと座標</h3>

<div class="formula-box">
<strong>空間座標の公式</strong>
<math display="block" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">|</mo><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">|</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mrow><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><msub><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>−</mo><msub><mi>x</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><msub><mi>y</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>−</mo><msub><mi>y</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><msub><mi>z</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>−</mo><msub><mi>z</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow></msqrt></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
|AB|=\sqrt{(x_2-x_1)^2+(y_2-y_1)^2+(z_2-z_1)^2}
</annotation></semantics></math>
<strong>球面の方程式</strong>（中心 <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>a</mi><mo>,</mo><mi>b</mi><mo>,</mo><mi>c</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">(a,b,c)</annotation></semantics></math>，半径 <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mi>r</mi><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">r</annotation></semantics></math>）：<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>−</mo><mi>a</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>y</mi><mo>−</mo><mi>b</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>z</mi><mo>−</mo><mi>c</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>r</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">(x-a)^2+(y-b)^2+(z-c)^2=r^2</annotation></semantics></math><br>
<strong>球面の一般形：</strong><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>y</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>z</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mi>l</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>m</mi><mi>y</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>n</mi><mi>z</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>d</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">x^2+y^2+z^2+lx+my+nz+d=0</annotation></semantics></math> は中心 <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mo>−</mo><mi>l</mi><mi>/</mi><mn>2</mn><mo>,</mo><mo>−</mo><mi>m</mi><mi>/</mi><mn>2</mn><mo>,</mo><mo>−</mo><mi>n</mi><mi>/</mi><mn>2</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">(-l/2,-m/2,-n/2)</annotation></semantics></math>，半径 <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><msqrt><mrow><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>l</mi><mi>/</mi><mn>2</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>m</mi><mi>/</mi><mn>2</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>n</mi><mi>/</mi><mn>2</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>−</mo><mi>d</mi></mrow></msqrt><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\sqrt{(l/2)^2+(m/2)^2+(n/2)^2-d}</annotation></semantics></math> の球（<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>&gt;</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">&gt;0</annotation></semantics></math> のとき）
</div>
</div><!-- /s4-3 -->

<!-- 4.4 -->

<div class="section" id="s4-4">
<h3>4.4 直線・平面の方程式</h3>

<div class="formula-box theorem">
<strong>空間の直線・平面の方程式</strong>
<div class="table-wrap"><table>
  <tr><th>図形</th><th>方程式</th><th>条件</th></tr>
  <tr><td>直線（点 <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mi>A</mi><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">A</annotation></semantics></math> + 方向 <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mover><mi>d</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\vec{d}</annotation></semantics></math>）</td><td><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mover><mi>p</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mover><mi>a</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>+</mo><mi>t</mi><mover><mi>d</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\vec{p}=\vec{a}+t\vec{d}</annotation></semantics></math></td><td><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>t</mi><mo>∈</mo><mi>ℝ</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">t\in\mathbb{R}</annotation></semantics></math></td></tr>
  <tr><td>直線（2点 <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>A</mi><mo>,</mo><mi>B</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">A,B</annotation></semantics></math>）</td><td><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mover><mi>p</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mi>t</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mover><mi>a</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>+</mo><mi>t</mi><mover><mi>b</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\vec{p}=(1-t)\vec{a}+t\vec{b}</annotation></semantics></math></td><td></td></tr>
  <tr><td>平面（点 <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mi>A</mi><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">A</annotation></semantics></math> + 法線 <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mover><mi>n</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\vec{n}</annotation></semantics></math>）</td><td><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mover><mi>n</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>⋅</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mover><mi>p</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>−</mo><mover><mi>a</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\vec{n}\cdot(\vec{p}-\vec{a})=0</annotation></semantics></math></td><td>成分形：<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>l</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>−</mo><msub><mi>a</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>+</mo><mi>⋯</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">l(x-a_1)+\cdots=0</annotation></semantics></math></td></tr>
  <tr><td>点と平面の距離</td><td><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>D</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">|</mo><mi>a</mi><msub><mi>x</mi><mn>0</mn></msub><mo>+</mo><mi>b</mi><msub><mi>y</mi><mn>0</mn></msub><mo>+</mo><mi>c</mi><msub><mi>z</mi><mn>0</mn></msub><mo>+</mo><mi>d</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">|</mo></mrow><msqrt><mrow><msup><mi>a</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>b</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>c</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow></msqrt></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">D=\dfrac{|ax_0+by_0+cz_0+d|}{\sqrt{a^2+b^2+c^2}}</annotation></semantics></math></td><td>平面 <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>a</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>b</mi><mi>y</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>c</mi><mi>z</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>d</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">ax+by+cz+d=0</annotation></semantics></math></td></tr>
</table></div>
</div>

<div class="example-box">
<strong>例題 4.3</strong> <span class="lv lv-m">標準</span>　3点 <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>A</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>0</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">A(1,0,0)</annotation></semantics></math>，<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>B</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>0</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">B(0,1,0)</annotation></semantics></math>，<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>C</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">C(0,0,1)</annotation></semantics></math> を通る平面の方程式と，原点 <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mi>O</mi><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">O</annotation></semantics></math> からの距離を求めよ。
<div class="answer-block">
3点を通るので平面の方程式を <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>a</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>b</mi><mi>y</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>c</mi><mi>z</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">ax+by+cz=1</annotation></semantics></math> とおく（定数項 <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">=1</annotation></semantics></math>）。<br>
<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mi>A</mi><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">A</annotation></semantics></math>：<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>a</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">a=1</annotation></semantics></math>，<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mi>B</mi><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">B</annotation></semantics></math>：<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>b</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">b=1</annotation></semantics></math>，<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mi>C</mi><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">C</annotation></semantics></math>：<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>c</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">c=1</annotation></semantics></math>。平面の方程式：<strong><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>y</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>z</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">x+y+z=1</annotation></semantics></math></strong><br><br>
点 <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>O</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>0</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">O(0,0,0)</annotation></semantics></math> から平面 <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>y</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>z</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">x+y+z-1=0</annotation></semantics></math> への距離：<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>D</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">|</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">|</mo></mrow><msqrt><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msqrt></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mn>1</mn><msqrt><mn>3</mn></msqrt></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><msqrt><mn>3</mn></msqrt><mn>3</mn></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">D=\dfrac{|0+0+0-1|}{\sqrt{1+1+1}}=\dfrac{1}{\sqrt{3}}=\dfrac{\sqrt{3}}{3}</annotation></semantics></math>
</div>
</div>
</div><!-- /s4-4 -->

<!-- 4.5 -->

<div class="section" id="s4-5">
<h3>4.5 外積・四面体の体積</h3>

<div class="formula-box definition">
<strong>外積（クロス積）の定義</strong>
<math display="block" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mover><mi>a</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>×</mo><mover><mi>b</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">∣</mo><mtable><mtr><mtd columnalign="center" style="text-align: center"><mover><mi>i</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover></mtd><mtd columnalign="center" style="text-align: center"><mover><mi>j</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover></mtd><mtd columnalign="center" style="text-align: center"><mover><mi>k</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd columnalign="center" style="text-align: center"><msub><mi>a</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mtd><mtd columnalign="center" style="text-align: center"><msub><mi>a</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mtd><mtd columnalign="center" style="text-align: center"><msub><mi>a</mi><mn>3</mn></msub></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd columnalign="center" style="text-align: center"><msub><mi>b</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mtd><mtd columnalign="center" style="text-align: center"><msub><mi>b</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mtd><mtd columnalign="center" style="text-align: center"><msub><mi>b</mi><mn>3</mn></msub></mtd></mtr></mtable><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">∣</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><msub><mi>a</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi>b</mi><mn>3</mn></msub><mo>−</mo><msub><mi>a</mi><mn>3</mn></msub><msub><mi>b</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>,</mo><mspace width="0.278em"></mspace><msub><mi>a</mi><mn>3</mn></msub><msub><mi>b</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>−</mo><msub><mi>a</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><msub><mi>b</mi><mn>3</mn></msub><mo>,</mo><mspace width="0.278em"></mspace><msub><mi>a</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><msub><mi>b</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>−</mo><msub><mi>a</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi>b</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
\vec{a}\times\vec{b}=\begin{vmatrix}\vec{i}&amp;\vec{j}&amp;\vec{k}\\a_1&amp;a_2&amp;a_3\\b_1&amp;b_2&amp;b_3\end{vmatrix}=(a_2b_3-a_3b_2,\;a_3b_1-a_1b_3,\;a_1b_2-a_2b_1)
</annotation></semantics></math>
</div>

<div class="formula-box theorem">
<strong>外積の性質</strong>
<ul class="bullet">
  <li><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mover><mi>a</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>×</mo><mover><mi>b</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>⊥</mo><mover><mi>a</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\vec{a}\times\vec{b}\perp\vec{a}</annotation></semantics></math> かつ <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mover><mi>a</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>×</mo><mover><mi>b</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>⊥</mo><mover><mi>b</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\vec{a}\times\vec{b}\perp\vec{b}</annotation></semantics></math>（両方に垂直）</li>
  <li><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">|</mo><mover><mi>a</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>×</mo><mover><mi>b</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">|</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">|</mo><mover><mi>a</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">|</mo></mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">|</mo><mover><mi>b</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">|</mo></mrow><mo>sin</mo><mi>θ</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">|\vec{a}\times\vec{b}|=|\vec{a}||\vec{b}|\sin\theta</annotation></semantics></math>（平行四辺形の面積）</li>
  <li><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mover><mi>a</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>×</mo><mover><mi>b</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mo>−</mo><mover><mi>b</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>×</mo><mover><mi>a</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\vec{a}\times\vec{b}=-\vec{b}\times\vec{a}</annotation></semantics></math>（反交換性）</li>
  <li><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mover><mi>a</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>∥</mo><mover><mi>b</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>⇔</mo><mover><mi>a</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>×</mo><mover><mi>b</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mover><mn>0</mn><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\vec{a}\parallel\vec{b}\Leftrightarrow\vec{a}\times\vec{b}=\vec{0}</annotation></semantics></math></li>
  <li>三角形の面積：<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>S</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">|</mo><mover><mi>a</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>×</mo><mover><mi>b</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">|</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">S=\dfrac{1}{2}|\vec{a}\times\vec{b}|</annotation></semantics></math></li>
</ul>
<strong>スカラー三重積と四面体の体積：</strong>
<math display="block" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>V</mi><mtext mathvariant="normal">四面体</mtext></msub><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>6</mn></mfrac><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">|</mo><mover><mi>a</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>⋅</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mover><mi>b</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>×</mo><mover><mi>c</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">|</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
V_{\text{四面体}}=\frac{1}{6}|\vec{a}\cdot(\vec{b}\times\vec{c})|
</annotation></semantics></math>
</div>

<div class="proof-box">
<strong><math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">|</mo><mover><mi>a</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>×</mo><mover><mi>b</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">|</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">|</mo><mover><mi>a</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">|</mo></mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">|</mo><mover><mi>b</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">|</mo></mrow><mo>sin</mo><mi>θ</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">|\vec{a}\times\vec{b}|=|\vec{a}||\vec{b}|\sin\theta</annotation></semantics></math> の証明：</strong><br>
<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">|</mo><mover><mi>a</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>×</mo><mover><mi>b</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">|</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><msub><mi>a</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi>b</mi><mn>3</mn></msub><mo>−</mo><msub><mi>a</mi><mn>3</mn></msub><msub><mi>b</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><msub><mi>a</mi><mn>3</mn></msub><msub><mi>b</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>−</mo><msub><mi>a</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><msub><mi>b</mi><mn>3</mn></msub><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><msub><mi>a</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><msub><mi>b</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>−</mo><msub><mi>a</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi>b</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">|\vec{a}\times\vec{b}|^2=(a_2b_3-a_3b_2)^2+(a_3b_1-a_1b_3)^2+(a_1b_2-a_2b_1)^2</annotation></semantics></math> を展開すると：
<math display="block" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>=</mo><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">|</mo><mover><mi>a</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">|</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">|</mo><mover><mi>b</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">|</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>−</mo><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><msub><mi>a</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><msub><mi>b</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>+</mo><msub><mi>a</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi>b</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>+</mo><msub><mi>a</mi><mn>3</mn></msub><msub><mi>b</mi><mn>3</mn></msub><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">|</mo><mover><mi>a</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">|</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">|</mo><mover><mi>b</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">|</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>−</mo><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mover><mi>a</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>⋅</mo><mover><mi>b</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">|</mo><mover><mi>a</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">|</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">|</mo><mover><mi>b</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">|</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><msup><mo>cos</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mi>θ</mi><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">|</mo><mover><mi>a</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">|</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><msup><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">|</mo><mover><mi>b</mi><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">|</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><msup><mo>sin</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mi>θ</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
=|\vec{a}|^2|\vec{b}|^2-(a_1b_1+a_2b_2+a_3b_3)^2=|\vec{a}|^2|\vec{b}|^2-(\vec{a}\cdot\vec{b})^2=|\vec{a}|^2|\vec{b}|^2(1-\cos^2\theta)=|\vec{a}|^2|\vec{b}|^2\sin^2\theta
</annotation></semantics></math>
<div class="qed">■</div>
</div>

<div class="exam-card">
<div class="exam-hd"><span>入試問題（阪大・改）</span><span class="etag tag-vec">ベクトル</span></div>
<div class="exam-body">
<p>空間に4点 <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>O</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>0</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">O(0,0,0)</annotation></semantics></math>，<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>A</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>0</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">A(1,0,0)</annotation></semantics></math>，<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>B</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>0</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">B(0,1,0)</annotation></semantics></math>，<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>C</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">C(0,0,1)</annotation></semantics></math> がある。</p>
<p>(1) <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>△</mi><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\triangle ABC</annotation></semantics></math> の面積を求めよ。&emsp; (2) 四面体 <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>O</mi><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">OABC</annotation></semantics></math> の体積を求めよ。</p>
<div class="answer-block">
(1) <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mover><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi></mrow><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>0</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\overrightarrow{AB}=(-1,1,0)</annotation></semantics></math>，<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mover><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>C</mi></mrow><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\overrightarrow{AC}=(-1,0,1)</annotation></semantics></math><br>
<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mover><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi></mrow><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>×</mo><mover><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>C</mi></mrow><mo accent="true">→</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>⋅</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>⋅</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>,</mo><mspace width="0.278em"></mspace><mn>0</mn><mo>⋅</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>−</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>⋅</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>,</mo><mspace width="0.278em"></mspace><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>⋅</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>⋅</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\overrightarrow{AB}\times\overrightarrow{AC}=(1\cdot 1-0\cdot 0,\;0\cdot(-1)-(-1)\cdot 1,\;(-1)\cdot 0-1\cdot(-1))=(1,1,1)</annotation></semantics></math><br>
<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>S</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">|</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">|</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><msqrt><mn>3</mn></msqrt><mn>2</mn></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">S=\dfrac{1}{2}|(1,1,1)|=\dfrac{\sqrt{3}}{2}</annotation></semantics></math><br><br>
(2) 法線ベクトル <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo stretchy="true" form="prefix">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="true" form="postfix">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">(1,1,1)</annotation></semantics></math> より平面 <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">ABC</annotation></semantics></math>：<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>y</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>z</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">x+y+z=1</annotation></semantics></math>。原点からの距離 <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>h</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mn>1</mn><msqrt><mn>3</mn></msqrt></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">h=\dfrac{1}{\sqrt{3}}</annotation></semantics></math>。<br>
<math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>V</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mn>1</mn><mn>3</mn></mfrac><mo>⋅</mo><mi>S</mi><mo>⋅</mo><mi>h</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mn>1</mn><mn>3</mn></mfrac><mo>⋅</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><msqrt><mn>3</mn></msqrt><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>⋅</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mn>1</mn><msqrt><mn>3</mn></msqrt></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac displaystyle="true"><mn>1</mn><mn>6</mn></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">V=\dfrac{1}{3}\cdot S\cdot h=\dfrac{1}{3}\cdot\dfrac{\sqrt{3}}{2}\cdot\dfrac{1}{\sqrt{3}}=\dfrac{1}{6}</annotation></semantics></math>
</div>
</div>
</div>
